English: You're feeling fast and furious!\n[c][FF0000]Movement speed is increased by 50% and maximum stamina increased
Chinese (simplified): 你感觉快速而愤怒，\n[c][FF0000]移动速度增加50%，最大耐力增加[-][/c]

English: What the hell did I just drink?\n[c][00FF80]Complete immunity to temperature, Slow Radiation reduction, Slow health regeneration
Chinese (simplified): 我刚刚到底喝了什么?\n[c][00FF80]完全免疫温度，缓慢减少辐射，缓慢恢复健康[-][/c]

English: Strawberry, Yum!\n[c][FF6666]Health regenerates. Maximum health and stamina increased!
Chinese (simplified): 草莓，美味！\n[c][FF6666]健康恢复。最大生命值和耐力增加！[-][/c]

English: I feel really weird right now...\n[c][008FFF]Movement speed increased to 250%, Maximum stamina increased, Rapid hunger loss
Chinese (simplified): 我现在感觉真的很奇怪...\n[c][008FFF]移动速度增加到250%，最大耐力增加，饥饿快速减少[-][/c]

English: This... is just water?\n[c][7FF9FF]Minor stamina and health regeneration with reduced hunger loss
Chinese (simplified): 这这仅仅是水吗?\n[c][7FF9FF]轻微的耐力和健康恢复，饥饿损失减少[-][/c]

English: Not bad...\n[FFFF00]Hunger is being restored, Stamina... not so much.
Chinese (simplified): 不错啊...\n[c][FFFF00]饥饿正在恢复，精力...没那么多。[-][/c]

English: [c][FF0000]Rapidly restores 500 health[-][/c] \nA medical apparatus that attaches to an exposed limb to rapidly reconstruct damage tissue faster than any other medical injector on the market.
Deutsch: Stellt ungefähr 500 Gesundheit wieder her. Benutzung aus Schnellzugriff via LMT und aus Inventar via Shift+RMT.
Français: Restaure environ 500 points de santé. Peut être utilisé depuis la barre outils [Clic gauche] ou depuis l'inventaire [Maj+Clic droit].
Italiano: Ripristina circa 500 punti salute. Utilizza con PSM dalla barra strumenti o dall'inventario con Maiusc+PDM.
Spanish: Restaura alrededor de 500 de salud. Úsalo con BIR desde la barra de herramientas o desde el inventario con Shift+BDR.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]快速恢复500点生命值[-][/c] \n这是一种医疗设备，可以连接到暴露的肢体上，以比市场上任何其他医疗注射器更快地快速修复受损组织。

English: A hot and spicy soup with a delicate flavor and a faintly sweet aftertaste. Traditionally a Tal'on dish that has gained galactic popularity over the last decade.\n[c][FFEE80]Recovers health and Increases body temperature
Deutsch: Eine scharf-würzige Suppe mit einem feinen Geschmack und einem leicht süßlichen Nachgeschmack. Traditionell ein Tal'on-Gericht, das in den letzten zehn Jahren galaktisch an Popularität gewonnen hat.
Français: Une soupe chaude et épicée avec une saveur délicate et un arrière-goût légèrement sucré. Traditionnellement un plat Tal'on qui a gagné en popularité galactique au cours de la dernière décennie.
Italiano: Una zuppa calda e piccante dal sapore delicato e dal retrogusto leggermente dolce. Tradizionalmente un piatto Tal'on che ha guadagnato popolarità galattica nell'ultimo decennio.
Spanish: Una sopa caliente y picante con un sabor delicado y un regusto ligeramente dulce. Tradicionalmente un plato de Tal'on que ha ganado popularidad galáctica durante la última década.
Chinese (simplified): 一种起源于泰隆带有无穷回味的香辣汤，近几年来广受各种族好评\n[c][ffee80]回复生命并提升体温[-][/c]

English: A fresh salad composed of Ziraxian red cabbage, Omicronian Daikon, and topped with grilled Ignidon meat.\n[c][B2FF80]Slowly recovers health and increases maximum health
Deutsch: Ein frischer Salat aus Ziraxian-Rotkohl, Omicronian Daikon und gegrilltem Ignidon-Fleisch.
Français: Une salade fraîche composée de chou rouge Ziraxian, Omicronian Daikon, et garnie de viande d'Ignidon grillée.
Italiano: Una fresca insalata composta da cavolo rosso Ziraxian, Omicroniano Daikon e condita con carne di Ignidon alla griglia.
Spanish: Una ensalada fresca compuesta de col lombarda de Ziraxian, Omicronian Daikon, y cubierta con carne Ignidon a la parrilla.
Chinese (simplified): 一份新鲜的沙拉，主料为兹瑞克斯红卷心菜和奥米克戎萝卜，佐以喷火牛肉\n[c][B2FF80]缓慢回复生命并提升生命上限[-][/c]

English: A mix of Leafcutter meat, Oscatunian Cabbage, and long chewy noodles in a shoyu broth base. This Ramen can only be prepared by a master chef.\n[c][FFF1AA]Regenerates health slowly, reduces hunger loss and increases maximum health
Deutsch: Eine Mischung aus Blattschneiderfleisch, Oscatunian Kohl und langen, zähen Nudeln in einer Shoyu-Brühe. Dieser Ramen kann nur von einem Meisterkoch zubereitet werden.
Français: Un mélange de viande de coupe-feuille, de chou oscatunien et de longues nouilles moelleuses dans une base de bouillon shoyu. Ce Ramen ne peut être préparé que par un maître cuisinier.
Italiano: Un mix di carne tagliafoglie, cavolo oscatuniano e lunghi noodles gommosi in una base di brodo shoyu. Questo Ramen può essere preparato solo da un maestro chef.
Spanish: Una mezcla de carne de cortador de hojas, repollo de Oscatunian y fideos largos y masticables en una base de caldo shoyu. Este Ramen solo puede ser preparado por un maestro de cocina.
Chinese (simplified): 叶刀肉、奥斯卡图尼亚卷心菜和耐嚼的长面条混合在酱油汤底中。这碗拉面只能由一位大师厨师准备。\n[c][FFF1AA]缓慢恢复生命值，减少饥饿感并增加最大生命值[-][/c]

English: Ice cold chocolate chip Ice cream. Eat it before it melts!\n[c][008FFF]Recovers stamina and rapidly reduces body temperature. Good on hot planets!
Deutsch: Eiskaltes Schokoladeneis. Essen Sie es, bevor es schmilzt!
Français: Glace glacée aux pépites de chocolat. Mangez-le avant qu'il ne fonde!
Italiano: Gelato con gocce di cioccolato ghiacciato. Mangialo prima che si sciolga!
Spanish: Helado helado de chispas de chocolate. ¡Cómelo antes de que se derrita!
Chinese (simplified): 冰冷的巧克力碎片冰淇淋。在它融化之前吃掉它！\n[c][008FFF]恢复体力和迅速降低体温。在炎热的星球上食用效果更佳！[-][/c]

English: [c][008FFF]Recovering stamina and rapidly reducing body temperature. Good on hot planets!
Deutsch: [c][008FFF]Wiederherstellung der Ausdauer und schnelle Reduzierung der Körpertemperatur.
Français: [c][008FFF]Récupération de l'endurance et réduction rapide de la température corporelle.
Italiano: [c][008FFF]Recuperare la resistenza e ridurre rapidamente la temperatura corporea.
Spanish: [c][008FFF]Recuperando la resistencia y reduciendo rápidamente la temperatura corporal.
Chinese (simplified): [c][008FFF]恢复体力和快速降低体温。在炎热的星球上效果不错！[-][/c]

English: [c][FFF1AA]Slowly regenerates health and reduces hunger loss. Increases maximum health!
Deutsch: [c][FFF1AA]Regeneriert langsam die Gesundheit und reduziert den Hungerverlust
Français: [c][FFF1AA]Régénère lentement la santé et réduit la perte de faim
Italiano: [c][FFF1AA]Rigenera lentamente la salute e riduce la perdita di fame
Spanish: [c][FFF1AA]Regenera lentamente la salud y reduce la pérdida de hambre
Chinese (simplified): [c][FFF1AA]缓慢恢复生命值并减少饥饿感的损失。增加最大生命值！[-][/c]

English: [c][B2FF80]Slowly recovers health and increases maximum health and stamina
Deutsch: [c][B2FF80]Stellt langsam Gesundheit und schnell Ausdauer wieder her
Français: [c][B2FF80]Récupère lentement la santé et récupère rapidement l'endurance
Italiano: [c][B2FF80]Recupera lentamente la salute e recupera rapidamente la resistenza
Spanish: [c][B2FF80]Recupera lentamente la salud y recupera rápidamente la resistencia.
Chinese (simplified): [c][B2FF80]缓慢恢复生命值，并增加最大生命值和耐力[-][/c]

Deutsch: [c][FFEE80]Stellt die Gesundheit wieder her und erhöht die Körpertemperatur
Français: [c][FFEE80]Récupère la santé et augmente la température corporelle
Italiano: [c][FFEE80]Recupera la salute e aumenta la temperatura corporea
Spanish: [c][FFEE80]Recupera la salud y aumenta la temperatura corporal

English: A laser PDW Submachine Gun developed by the Zirax after examining UCH weapons retrieved from the Titan's Wreckage.\n[c][FF0000]The technology to repair this weapon does not exist yet.
Deutsch: Eine kleinkalibrige PDW-Maschinenpistole, die von Zirax entwickelt wurde, nachdem UCH-Waffen untersucht wurden, die aus dem Wrack des Titans geborgen wurden.\n[c][FF0000]Die Technologie zur Reparatur dieser Waffe existiert noch nicht.
Français: Une mitraillette PDW de petit calibre développée par le Zirax après avoir examiné les armes UCH récupérées dans l'épave du Titan.\n[c][FF0000]La technologie pour réparer cette arme n'existe pas encore.
Italiano: Una mitragliatrice PDW di piccolo calibro sviluppata dallo Zirax dopo aver esaminato le armi UCH recuperate dal Relitto del Titano.\n[c][FF0000]La tecnologia per riparare quest'arma non esiste ancora.
Spanish: Una metralleta PDW de pequeño calibre desarrollada por Zirax después de examinar las armas de la UCH recuperadas de los restos del Titán.\n[c][FF0000]La tecnología para reparar esta arma aún no existe.
Chinese (simplified): 兹瑞克斯在仔细研究UCH坠落飞船中的武器数据后后研发的激光单兵自卫武器\n[c][FF0000]该武器无法维修[-][/c]

English: Some kind of unstable material that's a synthesis of both organic and synthetic. It's still... active and alive. I don't think I should touch it.\n[c][00AAFF]Reactive Xenomatter can be deconstructed into inactive Xenomaterial for use in Xenosteel.
Deutsch: Eine Art instabiles Material, das eine Synthese aus organischem und synthetischem Material ist. Es ist immer noch... aktiv und lebendig. Ich glaube nicht, dass ich es anfassen sollte.\n[c][00AAFF]Reaktives Xenomatter kann für die Verwendung in Xenosteel in inaktives Xenomaterial zerlegt werden.
Français: Une sorte de matériau instable qui est une synthèse à la fois organique et synthétique. Il est toujours... actif et vivant. Je ne pense pas que je devrais y toucher.\n[c][00AAFF]Le Xenomatter réactif peut être déconstruit en Xenomaterial inactif pour être utilisé dans Xenosteel.
Italiano: Una specie di materiale instabile che è una sintesi sia di organico che di sintetico. È ancora... attivo e vivo. Non credo che dovrei toccarlo.\n[c][00AAFF]La xenomateria reattiva può essere decostruita in xenomateriale inattivo per l'uso in Xenosteel.
Spanish: Algún tipo de material inestable que es una síntesis de lo orgánico y lo sintético. Todavía está ... activo y vivo. No creo que deba tocarlo.\n[c][00AAFF]El Xenomatter reactivo se puede deconstruir en Xenomaterial inactivo para su uso en Xenosteel.
Chinese (simplified): 某种同时具有有机体和合成物性质的材料，就像...活着一样，我不认为我应该触碰它.\n[c][00AAFF]可以在拆解机里拆分为异种基底[-][/c]

English: A standard-issue 9mm sidearm for UCH personnel for defense.\n[c][00AAFF]Rated for use underwater
Chinese (simplified): UCH人员用于防御的标准9毫米手枪。\n[c][00AAFF]水下使用等级[-][/c]

English: A basic pump-action shotgun that's standard issue for UCH tactical personnel in close quarters combat.
Chinese (simplified): 一种基本的泵动式霰弹枪，是UCH战术人员在近战中的标配武器。

English: A portable, multi-barreled rotary cannon for manned emplacements. This weapon has safeties in place to prevent personal injury.\n[c][FF0000]Hold LMB + RMB to fire at maximum speed.
Chinese (simplified): 一种便携式多管旋转炮，用于载人部署。这种武器设有安全装置以防止人员受伤。\n[c][FF0000]按住LMB + RMB以最大速度射击。[-][/c]

English: A fully-automatic combat rifle used by UCH military personnel as the standard-issue weapon.
Chinese (simplified): UCH战斗单位配发的标准自动武器

English: A long ranged anti-personnel and anti-materiel rifle weapon with a telescopic sight that has become the standard LRSW of the UCH.
Chinese (simplified): 装有瞄准镜的远程反人员武器，UCH将其作为标准狙击枪使用

English: An advanced semi-automatic combat shotgun used by elite UCH personnel for close quarters combat. It has a larger magazine and more stopping power than it's standard issue counterpart.
Chinese (simplified): 一种先进的半自动战斗霰弹枪，由精英UCH人员用于近战。与标准配备的同类武器相比，它拥有更大的弹匣容量和更强的停止能力。

English: A modified and enlarged MGL designed to operate using microrockets for anti-aircraft engagements or where the targets are protected behind armor. [c][00AAFF]Instantly destroys drones with a strike to critical components.
Chinese (simplified): 一种经过改进和放大的MGL，设计用于使用微型火箭进行防空交战或目标被装甲保护的地方。

English: Utilizing a pulsed laser array this weapon can produce collimated hard light beams that ignore atmospheric density and deal extreme thermal damage to the target.
Chinese (simplified): 使用脉冲激光阵列，这种武器能够产生准直的硬光束，这些光束无视大气密度，并对目标造成极端的热能伤害。

English: A lightweight, squad automatic weapon that's standard issue for UCH military and tactical personnel for rear support. It has superior range and damage over speed.
Chinese (simplified): 轻量化的UCH班用自动武器，主要配发给后勤支援部队，相比于射速更注重于威力和射程

English: Utilizing a pulsed laser array this weapon can produce collimated hard light beams that ignore atmospheric density and deal extreme thermal damage to the target.
Chinese (simplified): 使用脉冲激光阵列，这种武器能够产生准直的硬光束，这些光束无视大气密度，并对目标造成极端的热能伤害。

English: An experimental energy weapon that uses a concave laser array to superheat a cell of Erestrum Gel into plasma and propel it using electromagnetic fields towards a target.\n[c][00AAFF]Has two firing modes
Chinese (simplified): 一种实验性能量武器，使用凹面激光阵列将锷凝胶的单元超热至等离子体状态，并利用电磁场将其推向目标。

English: The upgraded version of the Standard Shield Generator. It can deflect almost any kinetic weapon with minimal energy expenditure and withstand direct strikes from heavy plasma weaponry.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.[-][/c]

English: A 10-tube rapid-fire, Multiple Rocket Launcher designed for use as a fixed armament for the UCH's Light Cruisers and Frigates for bombardment rather than precise targeting.\n[c][00BB00]Can be used in atmosphere at a reduced rate of fire with RMB[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields

English: [c][00FF00]Increases Maximum CPU Limit[-][/c]\nSome form of computing hardware that appears to have originated from The Legacy. Although it seemingly has no limits, you should use with caution.\n[c][FF0000]The possession and use of Legacy Technology is forbidden under Galactic Law due to its corruptive nature.

English: A self-targeting vehicle-mounted Surface-to-Air MRL that fires a full salvo of SAM-224 Homing Missiles per launch at either aircraft or ground installations with unrivalled accuracy.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields
Chinese (simplified): 自动跟踪车载地对空多管火箭发射器，每次发射时，无论是在飞机上还是在地面设施上，都能以无可匹敌的精度发射SAM-224跟踪导弹.\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A forward-facing bomb launcher used for aerial bombardments of enemy fortification with Mk.122 Bunker-busting Bombs.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields

English: A medium-ranged vehicle-mounted flamethrower originally designed for clearing trees and brush for development but proved effective against wildlife and enemy combatants.\n[c][FF0000]No Damage vs Energy Shields
Chinese (simplified): 一种中等射程车载火焰喷射器，最初设计用于清理树木和灌木丛以进行开发，但经证明对野生动物和敌方战斗人员有效.\n[c][FF0000]无对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A repurposed Disruptor Cannon extracted from the remains of a Legacy ship's internal autofactory. While not as powerful as a Legacy-controlled turret, it is still capable of dealing catastrophic damage to armor and weapon, though lacks the ability to penetrate shields.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]The possession and use of Legacy Technology is forbidden under Galactic Law due to its corruptive nature.
Chinese (simplified): 一种从废旧的遗留者飞船上的自动工厂垃圾堆里回收来的破坏者加农炮，虽然不像遗留者控制的炮塔那么强力，但仍能对装甲和武器造成灾难性的伤害，缺乏对于护盾的穿透力.\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]银河系法律禁止拥有和使用遗留技术，因为其具有腐蚀性。[-][/c]

English: A ship-mounted Beam Cutter and Welder designed for the quick and precise salvage of space wrecks and the repair of surface damage. Although lacking the ability to accurately retrieve structural parts, it was deemed unnecessary since the sheer mass would render any ship immobile.\n[c][FF0000]Can Repair and Salvage Blocks (75% Salvage Rate)
Chinese (simplified): 一种船载光束切割机和焊接机，用于快速精确地打捞太空残骸和修复表面损伤。虽然缺乏准确回收结构部件的能力，(这被认为是不必要的，因为巨大的质量会使任何船只无法移动。)\n[c][FF0000]能修理和回收方块 (75% 回收率)[-][/c]

English: A single-load Torpedo launcher designed specifically for anti-ship combat in space. The massive torpedo size results in extremely slow reload times. Deals catastrophic damage to Capital Vessels.\n[c][00FF00]Can only be used in Space[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields
Chinese (simplified): 专为太空反舰作战设计的单装鱼雷发射器。巨大的鱼雷尺寸使装填时间非常长。对主力舰造成灾难性破坏。.\n[c][00FF00]只能在太空使用[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]

Chinese (simplified): 一种大型货物集装箱，具有物流连接性。\n[c][FFFFFF]尺寸:[-][/c] 4x4x4

English: An improvement over the standard Light Armor suit, the Improved Light Armor provides more protection and higher mobility over the more restrictive Medium Armor at the cost of modularity.\n\n[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify your suit.
Deutsch: Die verbesserte leichte Rüstung ist eine Verbesserung gegenüber dem Standard-Leichtpanzeranzug und bietet mehr Schutz und höhere Mobilität als die restriktivere mittlere Rüstung auf Kosten der Modularität.\n\n[c][00FF00]Ein Rüstungsschrank ist zum Ausrüsten oder Modifizieren erforderlich dein Anzug.
Français: Une amélioration par rapport à l'armure légère standard, l'armure légère améliorée offre plus de protection et une plus grande mobilité par rapport à l'armure moyenne plus restrictive au détriment de la modularité.\n\n[c][00FF00]Un casier d'armure est nécessaire pour équiper ou modifier votre costume.
Italiano: Un miglioramento rispetto all'armatura leggera standard, l'armatura leggera migliorata offre maggiore protezione e maggiore mobilità rispetto all'armatura media più restrittiva a scapito della modularità.\n\n[c][00FF00]È necessario un armadietto per armature per equipaggiare o modificare il tuo vestito.
Spanish: Una mejora sobre el traje de armadura ligera estándar, la armadura ligera mejorada proporciona más protección y mayor movilidad sobre la armadura media más restrictiva a costa de modularidad.\n\n[c][00FF00]Se requiere un armario de armadura para equipar o modificar tu traje.
Chinese (simplified): 对标准轻型护甲套装的改进，相对于基础版增强轻型护甲提供了更多的保护和更高的机动性，某些方面的功能甚至超过了中型装甲\\n\n[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲更衣箱以装备你的护甲[-][/c]

English: An improvement over the standard Medium Armor suit, the Reinforced Medium Armor provides more protection and higher mobility over its regular counterpart and even exceeds Heavy Armor in overall functionality\n\n[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify your suit.
Deutsch: Als Verbesserung gegenüber dem Standardanzug mit mittlerer Rüstung bietet die verstärkte mittlere Rüstung mehr Schutz und höhere Mobilität als ihr reguläres Gegenstück und übertrifft sogar die Gesamtfunktionalität der schweren Rüstung\n\n[c][00FF00]Ein Rüstungsschrank ist zum Ausrüsten oder Modifizieren erforderlich dein Anzug.
Français: Une amélioration par rapport à la combinaison standard à armure moyenne, l'armure moyenne renforcée offre plus de protection et une plus grande mobilité par rapport à son homologue ordinaire et dépasse même l'armure lourde dans la fonctionnalité globale\n\n[c][00FF00]Un casier d'armure est nécessaire pour équiper ou modifier votre costume.
Italiano: Un miglioramento rispetto all'armatura media standard, l'armatura media rinforzata offre maggiore protezione e maggiore mobilità rispetto alla sua controparte normale e supera persino l'armatura pesante nella funzionalità generale\n\n[c][00FF00]È necessario un armadietto per armature per equipaggiare o modificare il tuo vestito.
Spanish: Una mejora con respecto al traje de armadura media estándar, la armadura media reforzada proporciona más protección y mayor movilidad que su contraparte normal e incluso supera la armadura pesada en funcionalidad general\n\n[c][00FF00]Se requiere un armario de armadura para equipar o modificar tu traje.
Chinese (simplified): 对标准中型护甲套装的改进，相对于基础版增强中型护甲提供了更多的保护和更高的机动性，某些方面的功能甚至超过了重型护甲\n\n[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲更衣箱以装备你的护甲[-][/c]

English: An improvement over the standard Heavy Armor suit, the Advanced Heavy Armor is unparalleled in protection both from hostile threats and from the environment.\n\n[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify your suit.
Deutsch: Die Advanced Heavy Armor ist eine Verbesserung gegenüber dem Standard-Heavy Armor-Anzug und bietet einen unvergleichlichen Schutz sowohl vor feindlichen Bedrohungen als auch vor der Umwelt.\n\n[c][00FF00]Ein Rüstungsschrank ist erforderlich, um deinen Anzug auszurüsten oder zu modifizieren.
Français: Une amélioration par rapport à l'armure lourde standard, l'armure lourde avancée offre une protection inégalée contre les menaces hostiles et contre l'environnement.\n\n[c][00FF00]Un Armor Locker est nécessaire pour équiper ou modifier votre combinaison.
Italiano: Un miglioramento rispetto all'armatura pesante standard, l'armatura pesante avanzata non ha eguali in termini di protezione sia dalle minacce ostili che dall'ambiente.\n\n[c][00FF00]È necessario un Armadietto per armature per equipaggiare o modificare la tua armatura.
Spanish: Una mejora con respecto al traje de armadura pesada estándar, la armadura pesada avanzada no tiene paralelo en protección tanto contra amenazas hostiles como del medio ambiente.\n\n[c][00FF00]Se requiere un Armor Locker para equipar o modificar tu traje.
Chinese (simplified): 对标准重型护甲套装的改进，史诗重型护甲能够提供无与伦比的装甲抗性和环境适应性\n\n[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲更衣箱以装备你的护甲[-][/c]

English: A vehicle-mounted kinetic weapon that uses electromagnetically charged rails to propel a heavy metal slug at high-velocity towards a target.\n[c][FF0000]Low damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Eine fahrzeugmontierte kinetische Waffe, die elektromagnetisch geladene Schienen verwendet, um eine Schwermetallkugel mit hoher Geschwindigkeit auf ein Ziel zu schleudern.\n[c][FF0000]Kinetische Waffe: Kein Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Une arme cinétique montée sur véhicule qui utilise des rails chargés électromagnétiquement pour propulser une limace de métal lourd à grande vitesse vers une cible.\n[c][FF0000]Arme cinétique : aucun dommage contre les boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Un'arma cinetica montata su un veicolo che utilizza binari caricati elettromagneticamente per spingere un proiettile di metallo pesante ad alta velocità verso un bersaglio.\n[c][FF0000]Arma cinetica: nessun danno contro gli scudi energetici
Spanish: Un arma cinética montada en un vehículo que usa rieles cargados electromagnéticamente para propulsar una babosa de metal pesado a alta velocidad hacia un objetivo.\n[c][FF0000]Arma cinética: Sin daño contra escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一种机载动能武器，利用电磁轨道发射重型金属弹头\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A vehicle-mounted rotary chaingun that can fire medium-caliber rounds in rapid succession for anti-aircraft and anti-personnel combat.\n[c][00BB00]Reduced damage vs Turrets and Armor[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Low damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Ein am Fahrzeug montiertes rotierendes Kettengewehr, das in schneller Folge mittelkalibrige Geschosse für Flugabwehr- und Antipersonenkämpfe abfeuern kann.\n[c][00BB00]Reduzierter Schaden gegen Geschütztürme und Panzerung[-][/c]\n[ c][FF0000]Geringer Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Un chaingun rotatif monté sur véhicule qui peut tirer des obus de moyen calibre en succession rapide pour le combat anti-aérien et antipersonnel.\n[c][00BB00]Dégâts réduits contre les tourelles et les blindés[-][/c]\n[ c][FF0000]Faible dégâts vs Boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Una mitragliatrice rotante montata su un veicolo che può sparare proiettili di medio calibro in rapida successione per il combattimento antiaereo e antiuomo.\n[c][00BB00]Danni ridotti contro torrette e armature[-][/c]\n[ c][FF0000]Danno basso contro gli scudi energetici
Spanish: Un chaingun giratorio montado en un vehículo que puede disparar rondas de calibre medio en rápida sucesión para el combate antiaéreo y antipersonal.\n[c][00BB00]Daños reducidos contra torretas y blindaje[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Daño bajo frente a escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一种机载转管链炮，可以连续发射中口径反人员/防空弹药\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A fixed-mounting Directed Energy Weapon that uses a multi-phase cascade laser array to fire collimated hard light beams at a target at a high rate of fire, dealing high thermal damage.\n[c][00FF00]High Damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Eine fest montierte gerichtete Energiewaffe, die ein mehrphasiges Kaskaden-Laser-Array verwendet, um kollimierte harte Lichtstrahlen mit hoher Feuerrate auf ein Ziel abzufeuern und dabei hohen thermischen Schaden zu verursachen.\n[c][00FF00]Hoher Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Arme à énergie dirigée à montage fixe qui utilise un réseau laser en cascade multiphasé pour tirer des faisceaux lumineux collimatés sur une cible à une cadence de tir élevée, infligeant des dégâts thermiques élevés.\n[c][00FF00]Dégâts élevés contre boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Un'arma a energia diretta a montaggio fisso che utilizza un array laser a cascata multifase per sparare raggi di luce intensa collimati su un bersaglio ad alta velocità di fuoco, infliggendo un elevato danno termico.\n[c][00FF00]Danno elevato contro scudi energetici
Spanish: Un arma de energía dirigida de montaje fijo que utiliza una matriz láser en cascada multifásica para disparar rayos de luz dura colimados a un objetivo a una alta tasa de fuego, lo que inflige un gran daño térmico.\n[c][00FF00]Gran daño frente a escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一种机载前射定向能武器，利用多相级联激光阵列对目标快速发射准直激光，造成大量热能伤害\n[c][00FF00]高对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A vehicle-mounted explosive energy weapon that uses a cascade laser array to superheat Erestrum plasma suspended in a magnetic field and launch it at a designated target.\n[c][FFBB00]Medium Damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Eine in einem Fahrzeug montierte explosive Energiewaffe, die ein Kaskaden-Laser-Array verwendet, um das in einem Magnetfeld schwebende Erestrum-Plasma zu überhitzen und auf ein bestimmtes Ziel zu schleudern.\n[c][FFBB00]Mittelschwerer Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Une arme à énergie explosive montée sur véhicule qui utilise un réseau laser en cascade pour surchauffer le plasma d'Erestrum suspendu dans un champ magnétique et le lancer sur une cible désignée.\n[c][FFBB00]Dégâts moyens contre boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Un'arma energetica esplosiva montata su un veicolo che utilizza un array laser a cascata per surriscaldare il plasma di Erestrum sospeso in un campo magnetico e lanciarlo su un bersaglio designato.\n[c][FFBB00]Danno medio contro scudi energetici
Spanish: Un arma de energía explosiva montada en un vehículo que utiliza una matriz de láser en cascada para sobrecalentar el plasma Erestrum suspendido en un campo magnético y lanzarlo a un objetivo designado.\n[c][FFBB00]Daño medio contra escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一种机载爆炸能量武器，使用级联激光阵列对悬浮在磁场中的锷凝胶等离子体进行过热，并将其发射到指定目标。\n[c][FFBB00]中对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A vehicle-mounted, dumbfire rocket launcher designed for Air-to-Ground bombardment of enemy facilities, turrets, Supply lines and troops.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Ein fahrzeugmontierter, stummer Raketenwerfer, der für den Luft-Boden-Bombardement feindlicher Einrichtungen, Geschütztürme, Versorgungslinien und Truppen entwickelt wurde.\n[c][FF0000]Geringer Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Un lance-roquettes monté sur véhicule et conçu pour le bombardement air-sol des installations ennemies, des tourelles, des lignes de ravitaillement et des troupes.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields
Italiano: Un lanciarazzi muto montato su un veicolo progettato per il bombardamento aria-terra di strutture nemiche, torrette, linee di rifornimento e truppe.\n[c][FF0000]Danno ridotto contro scudi energetici

English: A spacecraft-mounted, homing missile launcher designed for Space-to-Space combat in high-speed combat engagements.\n[c][00FF00]Missiles will track the exact location your crosshairs were pointing at when the weapon is fired.[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields

Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]你的宇航服氧气罐被刺破了![-][/c]\n自动密封剂正在尝试修复漏洞。
[斜放型] 高级太阳能电池板1
[斜放型] 高级太阳能电池板2
[斜放型] 高级太阳能电池板3
[平放型] 高级太阳能电池板1
[平放型] 高级太阳能电池板2
[平放型] 高级太阳能电池板-适配器
[平放型] 高级太阳能电池板支架-底座

English: An ultra-sensitive solar panel with superior solar efficiency able to draw the maximum possible energy from sunlight, even refracted light to provided sustainable power.
Deutsch: Ein ultra-empfindliches Solarmodul mit überragender Solareffizienz, das in der Lage ist, die maximal mögliche Energie aus Sonnenlicht zu ziehen, sogar gebrochenes Licht, um nachhaltige Energie bereitzustellen.
Français: Un panneau solaire ultra-sensible avec une efficacité solaire supérieure capable de tirer le maximum d'énergie possible de la lumière du soleil, même de la lumière réfractée pour fournir une énergie durable.
Italiano: Un pannello solare ultrasensibile con un'efficienza solare superiore in grado di trarre la massima energia possibile dalla luce solare, anche dalla luce rifratta, per fornire energia sostenibile.
Spanish: Un panel solar ultrasensible con una eficiencia solar superior capaz de extraer la máxima energía posible de la luz solar, incluso la luz refractada, para proporcionar energía sostenible.
Chinese (simplified): 一种光敏性极强的太阳能电池板，甚至能够从夜间的折射光中持续获取能量

English: A coolant-lined superconducting cable made from a highly-refined Zascosium alloy mix designed to transfer power with zero transmission loss at the maximum possible speed.
Chinese (simplified): 一种由高度精炼的铡合金混合物制成的冷却液衬里超导电缆，设计用于以在最大可能速度下零损失地传输电力。

English: A Sathium-reinforced composite plating comprised of several layers of different materials with varying radioactive modulus that's used on commercial warp drives and fusion reactors.
Chinese (simplified): 一种钑增强复合装甲板，由多层不同材料组成，具有不同的放射性模量，用于商业翘曲驱动器和聚变反应堆。

English: A carbon-fluorine superfluid is sealed inside the microscopic pores of each cell that maximizes energy capture and attenuation.\nUsed in the production of high-quality solar panels and satellites.
Chinese (simplified): 一种碳-氟超流体被密封在每个单元的微观孔隙中，最大化能量捕获和衰减。\n用于生产高质量的太阳能板和卫星。

English: Drive thruster components used in the production of engines on long-haul freighters and battleships that are subject to higher stresses than normal thrusters.
Chinese (simplified): 驱动推进器部件，用于生产长途货船和战舰上的发动机，这些发动机比普通推进器承受更高的压力。

English: A stable, crystalline form of carbon that possesses good conductive properties among others. It's both a precursor to industrial diamond production and the manufacturer of graphene nanofiber material in high-end electronics.
Deutsch: Eine stabile, kristalline Form von Kohlenstoff, die unter anderem gute Leitfähigkeitseigenschaften besitzt. Es ist sowohl ein Vorläufer der industriellen Diamantproduktion als auch der Hersteller von Graphen-Nanofasermaterial in der High-End-Elektronik.
Français: Une forme stable et cristalline de carbone qui possède entre autres de bonnes propriétés conductrices. C'est à la fois un précurseur de la production industrielle de diamants et le fabricant de nanofibres de graphène dans l'électronique haut de gamme.
Italiano: Una forma stabile e cristallina di carbonio che possiede, tra le altre, buone proprietà conduttive. È sia un precursore della produzione industriale di diamanti che il produttore di materiale in nanofibra di grafene nell'elettronica di fascia alta.
Spanish: Una forma de carbono estable y cristalina que posee, entre otras, buenas propiedades conductoras. Es tanto un precursor de la producción industrial de diamantes como el fabricante de material de nanofibras de grafeno en la electrónica de alta gama.
Chinese (simplified): 一种稳定的晶体形态碳，具有良好的导电性等特性。它既是工业钻石生产的前体，也是高端电子设备中石墨烯纳米纤维材料的制造商。

English: A common and vital element used in everything from explosives to medical ingredients.\nAlthough common, it is always in demand throughout the galactic market.
Deutsch: Ein übliches und lebenswichtiges Element, das in allem verwendet wird, von Sprengstoffen bis hin zu medizinischen Inhaltsstoffen.\nObwohl es üblich ist, wird es immer auf dem gesamten galaktischen Markt nachgefragt.
Français: Un élément commun et vital utilisé dans tout, des explosifs aux ingrédients médicaux.\nBien que commun, il est toujours demandé sur tout le marché galactique.
Italiano: Un elemento comune e vitale utilizzato in tutto, dagli esplosivi agli ingredienti medici.\nAnche se comune, è sempre richiesto in tutto il mercato galattico.
Spanish: Un elemento común y vital que se usa en todo, desde explosivos hasta ingredientes médicos.\nAunque es común, siempre está en demanda en todo el mercado galáctico.
Chinese (simplified): 一种常见且至关重要的元素，用于从爆炸物到医疗成分的所有领域。\n尽管常见，但在整个银河市场中始终有需求。

English: Flat-packed Prefab Housing modules commonly used in the wake of environmental disasters or during the construction period of outlying colonies.\nThey're not the most spacious or comfortable, but it's better than a tent.
Chinese (simplified): 平板预制房屋模块，通常用于环境灾难后或边远殖民地建设期间。\n它们不是最宽敞或舒适的，但总比帐篷好。

English: The core module of a Fusion Reactor that contains not only the reaction chamber but the feed lines for the fuel, with enough shielding and coolant channels for use in compact generators.
Chinese (simplified): 一个聚变反应堆的核心模块，不仅包含反应室，还有燃料的供给线，有足够的屏蔽和冷却通道，适用于紧凑型发电机。

English: Unknown electronic components that comprise the inner workings of quantum computers. The technology is formulated at the picoscopic level up, making it impossible to replicate or even understand.
Chinese (simplified): 未知的电子组件，构成量子计算机的内部运作。该技术从微观层面上制定，使其无法复制或甚至理解。

English: An aluminium-palladium heat sink used to draw heat away from vital components and either disperse it or dump it into external coolant systems.
Chinese (simplified): 一种铝钯散热器，用于将热量从关键组件中吸走，然后将其分散或排入外部冷却系统。

English: An essential mineral used in everything from food to agriculture and numerous industrial applications.\nAlthough not particularly valuable, it is always in demand throughout the galactic market.
Deutsch: Ein essentielles Mineral, das in allem von der Nahrung über die Landwirtschaft bis hin zu zahlreichen industriellen Anwendungen verwendet wird.\nObwohl es nicht besonders wertvoll ist, ist es auf dem gesamten galaktischen Markt immer gefragt.
Français: Un minéral essentiel utilisé dans tout, de l'alimentation à l'agriculture et dans de nombreuses applications industrielles.\nBien qu'il ne soit pas particulièrement précieux, il est toujours en demande sur tout le marché galactique.
Italiano: Un minerale essenziale utilizzato in tutto, dal cibo all'agricoltura e in numerose applicazioni industriali.\nAnche se non particolarmente prezioso, è sempre richiesto in tutto il mercato galattico.
Spanish: Un mineral esencial que se utiliza en todo, desde la alimentación hasta la agricultura y numerosas aplicaciones industriales.\nAunque no es particularmente valioso, siempre tiene una demanda en todo el mercado galáctico.
Chinese (simplified): 一种必需的矿物，用于从食品到农业和许多工业应用的所有领域。\n尽管不是特别有价值，但在整个银河市场中始终有需求。

English: A packed and sealed case with standard equipment used by outlying colonies and mining rigs to extract resources from deep underground, beneath the bedrock layers.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装满并密封的标准设备箱，由边远殖民地和采矿设备用来从地下深处、基岩层以下提取资源。

English: A pressurized bottle of compressed helium typically used as fuel for low-yield Fusion Reactors and some older model thrusters that require propellant.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶压缩氦气，通常用作低产聚变反应堆的燃料，以及一些需要推进剂的旧型号推进器。

English: A pressurized bottle of liquid nitrogen, reinforced against the extreme cold of the fluid. It can be used to produce starship coolant and as a chemical agent in the use of fertilizers and explosives.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶加压的液态氮，加固以抵抗流体的极端寒冷。它可以用于生产星际飞船冷却剂，并作为肥料和爆炸物的化学剂。

English: A pressurized bottle of compressed Xenon Gas used in laser production and precision machinery as well as several medical applications.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶加压的氙气，用于激光生产、精密机械以及几种医疗应用。

English: A packed and sealed container of communication equipment used in the establishment of long-ranged communications with outlying colonies and deep space FTL coms.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装满并密封的通信设备容器，用于与边远殖民地和深空FTL通信建立远程通信。

English: The ZMX-404 is in simpler terms: A landmine.\nThe construction is fundamentally similar to UCH munitions of the same class but contains an electronic safety that reacts only to zirax bio-signatures. This is renders the weapon useless if stolen since it cannot be repurposed easily.
Chinese (simplified): ZMX-404简单来说是一种地雷。\n其构造基本上与UCH同类弹药相似，但包含一个电子安全装置，仅对兹瑞克斯生物特征反应。这使得武器如果被盗则无法轻易重新利用，因而变得无用。

English: Standard data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning civilian work orders, ship maintenance and economic data.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Standarddaten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert werden, das nach sensiblen Informationen zu zivilen Arbeitsaufträgen, Schiffswartung und Wirtschaftsdaten durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann an einigen Stationen an einen Informationsmakler verkauft werden
Français: Données standard extraites d'un système « sécurisé » pouvant être extraites des informations sensibles concernant les ordres de travail civils, la maintenance des navires et les données économiques.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Peut être vendu à un courtier en informations sur certaines stations
Italiano: Dati standard estratti da un sistema "sicuro" che possono essere estratti per informazioni sensibili relative a ordini di lavoro civili, manutenzione navale e dati economici.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Può essere venduto a un broker di informazioni su alcune stazioni
Chinese (simplified): 从“安全”系统中提取的标准数据，可以被数据挖掘以获取有关民用工作订单、船舶维护和经济数据的敏感信息。\n\n[c][FFBB00]可以在某些站点上出售给信息经纪人[-][/c]

English: Scientific data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning biological, ecological and archaeological surveys.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Wissenschaftliche Daten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert werden, das nach sensiblen Informationen zu biologischen, ökologischen und archäologischen Untersuchungen durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann an einigen Stationen an einen Informationsmakler verkauft werden
Français: Données scientifiques extraites d'un système "sécurisé" pouvant être data-mining pour des informations sensibles concernant les études biologiques, écologiques et archéologiques.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Peut être vendu à un Information Broker sur certaines stations
Italiano: Dati scientifici estratti da un sistema "sicuro" che possono essere estratti per informazioni sensibili relative a indagini biologiche, ecologiche e archeologiche.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Può essere venduto a un broker di informazioni su alcune stazioni
Chinese (simplified): 从“安全”系统中提取的科学数据，可以数据挖掘以获取有关生物、生态和考古调查的敏感信息。\n\n[c][FFBB00]可以在某些站点上出售给信息经纪人[-][/c]

English: Exploration data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning astronomic, geological and atmospheric data.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Explorationsdaten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert wurden, das nach sensiblen Informationen zu astronomischen, geologischen und atmosphärischen Daten durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann an einigen Stationen an einen Informationsbroker verkauft werden
Français: Données d'exploration extraites d'un système "sécurisé" qui peut être data-mining pour des informations sensibles concernant les données astronomiques, géologiques et atmosphériques.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Peut être vendu à un Information Broker sur certaines stations
Italiano: Dati di esplorazione estratti da un sistema "sicuro" che possono essere estratti per informazioni sensibili riguardanti dati astronomici, geologici e atmosferici.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Può essere venduto a un broker di informazioni su alcune stazioni
Chinese (simplified): 从“安全”系统中提取的探索数据，可以数据挖掘以获取有关天文、地质和大气数据的敏感信息。\n\n[c][FFBB00]可以在某些站点上出售给信息经纪人[-][/c]

English: Security data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning sector-specific warp and weapon signatures.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Sicherheitsdaten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert werden, das nach sensiblen Informationen zu sektorspezifischen Warp- und Waffensignaturen durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann auf einigen Stationen an einen Informationsbroker verkauft werden
Français: Données de sécurité extraites d'un système « sécurisé » qui peut être extrait pour des informations sensibles concernant les signatures de distorsion et d'armes spécifiques au secteur.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Peut être vendu à un courtier en informations sur certaines stations
Italiano: Dati di sicurezza estratti da un sistema "sicuro" che possono essere estratti per informazioni sensibili relative a warp e firme di armi specifiche del settore.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Può essere venduto a un broker di informazioni su alcune stazioni
Chinese (simplified): 从“安全”系统中提取的安全数据，可以数据挖掘以获取有关特定部门的翘曲和武器特征的敏感信息。\n\n[c][FFBB00]可以在某些站点上出售给信息经纪人[-][/c]

English: Military data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning military maneuvers, troop movements and surveillance.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Militärdaten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert werden, das nach sensiblen Informationen über Militärmanöver, Truppenbewegungen und Überwachung durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann auf einigen Stationen an einen Informationsbroker verkauft werden
Français: Données militaires extraites d'un système "sécurisé" pouvant être data-minées pour des informations sensibles concernant les manœuvres militaires, les mouvements de troupes et la surveillance.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Peut être vendu à un Information Broker sur certaines stations
Italiano: Dati militari estratti da un sistema "sicuro" che possono essere estratti per informazioni sensibili riguardanti manovre militari, movimenti di truppe e sorveglianza.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Può essere venduto a un broker di informazioni su alcune stazioni
Chinese (simplified): 从“安全”系统中提取的军事数据，可以数据挖掘以获取有关军事演习、部队调动和监视的敏感信息。\n\n[c][FFBB00]可以在某些站点上出售给信息经纪人[-][/c]

陆基阳电子束炮塔 (可伸缩)
车载阳电子束炮塔 (悬浮飞船)
车载阳电子束炮塔 (可伸缩)
帝国重型离子束加农炮

English: [c][66CCFF]Block Group[-][/c]: RMB to Access\nPositron Beam Turret: Large Heat Sink\n[c][FFBB00]Lightspeed Directed Energy Weapon: Medium Damage vs Energy Shields[-][/c]
Deutsch: [c][66CCFF]Gruppe blockieren[-][/c]: RMB für Zugriff\nPositronenstrahlturm: Großer Kühlkörper\n[c][FFBB00]Lichtgeschwindigkeitsgerichtete Energiewaffe: Mittlerer Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: [c][66CCFF]Groupe de blocs[-][/c]: RMB pour accéder\nTourelle à faisceau de positons: grand dissipateur de chaleur\n[c][FFBB00]Arme à énergie dirigée par la vitesse de la lumière : dégâts moyens contre boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: [c][66CCFF]Gruppo di blocchi[-][/c]: RMB per accedere\nTorretta a fascio di positroni: dissipatore di calore grande\n[c][FFBB00]Arma a energia diretta alla velocità della luce: danni medi contro scudi energetici
Spanish: [c][66CCFF]Grupo de bloques[-][/c]: RMB para acceder \nTorreta de rayos positrones: Disipador de calor grande\n[c][FFBB00] Arma de energía dirigida a la velocidad de la luz: Daño medio contra escudos de energía[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [c][66CCFF]方块组[-][/c]：右键访问\n正电子束炮塔：大型散热片\n[c][FFBB00]光速定向能武器：对能量护盾的中等伤害[-][/c]

English: A directed energy weapon that utilizes a chemical laser fired through a Pentaxium lens to produce a coherent stream of Positrons moving at light speed that annihilates electron bonds.\n[c][FFBB00]Medium Damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Eine gerichtete Energiewaffe, die einen chemischen Laser verwendet, der durch eine Pentaxium-Linse abgefeuert wird, um einen kohärenten Strom von Positronen zu erzeugen, der sich mit Lichtgeschwindigkeit bewegt und Elektronenbindungen vernichtet.\n[c][FFBB00]Mittlerem Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Une arme à énergie dirigée qui utilise un laser chimique tiré à travers une lentille Pentaxium pour produire un flux cohérent de positons se déplaçant à la vitesse de la lumière qui annihile les liaisons électroniques.\n[c][FFBB00]Dégâts moyens vs boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Un'arma a energia diretta che utilizza un laser chimico sparato attraverso una lente al Pentaxium per produrre un flusso coerente di positroni che si muove alla velocità della luce che annienta i legami elettronici.\n[c][FFBB00]Danno medio contro scudi energetici
Spanish: Un arma de energía dirigida que utiliza un láser químico disparado a través de una lente Pentaxium para producir una corriente coherente de positrones que se mueven a la velocidad de la luz y que aniquilan los enlaces de electrones.\n[c][FFBB00]Daño medio contra escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一种定向能武器，通过Pentaxium镜头发射化学激光，产生一束以光速运动的相干正电子流，用于湮灭电子键。\n[c][FFBB00]中等伤害对能量护盾[-][/c]

English: A disposable thermal cell that stores heat from high-output devices until it reaches maximum capacity and is ejected safely.
Deutsch: Eine Einweg-Thermozelle, die die Wärme von Hochleistungsgeräten speichert, bis sie die maximale Kapazität erreicht und sicher abgeführt wird.
Français: Une cellule thermique jetable qui stocke la chaleur des appareils à haut rendement jusqu'à ce qu'elle atteigne sa capacité maximale et soit éjectée en toute sécurité.
Italiano: Una cella termica usa e getta che immagazzina il calore dai dispositivi ad alto rendimento fino a quando non raggiunge la capacità massima e viene espulso in sicurezza.
Spanish: Una celda térmica desechable que almacena el calor de los dispositivos de alto rendimiento hasta que alcanza su capacidad máxima y se expulsa de manera segura.
Chinese (simplified): 一种一次性热能电池，能存储来自高输出设备的热量，直到达到最大容量并安全排出。

English: A special-issue zirax particle beam rifle. It possesses two firing modes that each fire a stream of plasma at the target at relative speeds.\nHeat build-up will eventually render the weapon inoperable.
Deutsch: Ein spezielles Zirax-Partikelstrahlgewehr. Es besitzt zwei Feuermodi, von denen jeder einen Plasmastrom mit relativer Geschwindigkeit auf das Ziel abfeuert.\nDie Hitzeentwicklung macht die Waffe schließlich funktionsunfähig.
Français: Un fusil à faisceau de particules en zirax en édition spéciale. Il possède deux modes de tir qui tirent chacun un jet de plasma sur la cible à des vitesses relatives.\nL'accumulation de chaleur finira par rendre l'arme inutilisable.
Italiano: Un fucile a raggio particellare Zirax di emissione speciale. Possiede due modalità di fuoco, ciascuna delle quali spara un flusso di plasma sul bersaglio a velocità relative.\nL'accumulo di calore alla fine renderà l'arma inutilizzabile.
Spanish: Un rifle de haz de partículas zirax de edición especial. Posee dos modos de disparo, cada uno de los cuales dispara una corriente de plasma al objetivo a velocidades relativas.\nLa acumulación de calor eventualmente dejará el arma inoperable.
Chinese (simplified): 一种特殊版本的锆石粒子束枪。它有两种射击模式，每种模式都会以相对速度向目标发射一束等离子流。热量累积最终会使武器无法使用。

English: A secondary capacitor dedicated to supplying reserve energy to a shield generator; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.
Deutsch: Ein Sekundärkondensator, der dazu bestimmt ist, einen Schildgenerator mit Reserveenergie zu versorgen; Erhöhung der Schildstärke auf Kosten der Schildladegeschwindigkeit.
Français: Un condensateur secondaire dédié à la fourniture d'énergie de réserve à un générateur de bouclier ; augmenter la force du bouclier au détriment de la vitesse de charge du bouclier.
Italiano: Un condensatore secondario dedicato a fornire energia di riserva a un generatore di schermatura; aumentando la forza dello scudo a scapito della velocità di carica dello scudo.
Spanish: Un condensador secundario dedicado a suministrar energía de reserva a un generador de pantalla; aumentando la fuerza del escudo a costa de la velocidad de carga del escudo.
Chinese (simplified): 一个专用于为护盾发生器提供储备能量的次级电容器；以牺牲护盾充能速度为代价来增加护盾强度。

English: A main power coupling and regulator that diverts higher charge to a shield generator; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.
Deutsch: Eine Hauptstromkopplung und ein Regler, der höhere Ladung zu einem Schildgenerator umleitet; Erhöhung der Schildladegeschwindigkeit auf Kosten der Schildstärke.
Français: Un couplage et un régulateur d'alimentation principaux qui détournent une charge plus élevée vers un générateur de bouclier ; augmenter la vitesse de charge du bouclier au détriment de la force du bouclier.
Italiano: Un accoppiamento e un regolatore di alimentazione principale che devia una carica maggiore a un generatore di schermatura; aumentando la velocità di carica dello scudo a scapito della forza dello scudo.
Spanish: Un regulador y un acoplamiento de potencia principal que desvía una carga más alta a un generador de escudo; aumentando la velocidad de carga del escudo a costa de la fuerza del escudo.
Chinese (simplified): 一个主要的电源耦合和调节器，将更高的电荷转移到护盾发生器；以护盾强度为代价增加护盾电荷速度。

Français: Tourelles lourdes à faisceau de positrons
Italiano: Torrette a raggio di positroni pesanti
Chinese (simplified): 重型正电子束炮塔 (主力舰)

English: A 150mm chrome-lined tank cannon designed to fire artillery-sized shells long distances with tremendous force.\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields
Deutsch: Eine verchromte 150-mm-Panzerkanone, die dafür ausgelegt ist, Granaten in Artilleriegröße mit enormer Kraft über große Entfernungen abzufeuern.\n[c][FF0000]Geringer Schaden gegen Energieschilde
Français: Un canon de char chromé de 150 mm conçu pour tirer des obus de la taille d'une artillerie sur de longues distances avec une force énorme.\n[c][FF0000]Faibles dégâts par rapport aux boucliers énergétiques
Italiano: Un cannone corazzato da 150 mm con rivestimento cromato progettato per sparare proiettili delle dimensioni di un'artiglieria a lunga distanza con una forza tremenda.\n[c][FF0000]Basso danno contro scudi energetici
Spanish: Un cañón de tanque revestido de cromo de 150 mm diseñado para disparar proyectiles del tamaño de una artillería a largas distancias con una fuerza tremenda.\n[c][FF0000]Daño bajo frente a escudos de energía
Chinese (simplified): 一门150mm炮管镀铬线膛炮，可以惊人的威力发射远程炮弹\n[c][FF0000]低对护盾伤害[-][/c]

English: A standard-issue Shield Generator designed to offer significant protection against kinetic and explosive impacts, but can be disrupted by energy-based weapons. Offers superior protection over the Compact Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.
Deutsch: Ein standardmäßiger Schildgenerator, der erheblichen Schutz vor kinetischen und explosiven Einschlägen bietet, aber durch energiebasierte Waffen gestört werden kann. Bietet überlegenen Schutz gegenüber dem Compact Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Widersteht kinetischen Waffen und Raketen, ist aber anfällig für Laser, Plasma und EMP.
Français: Un générateur de bouclier standard conçu pour offrir une protection significative contre les impacts cinétiques et explosifs, mais peut être perturbé par des armes à base d'énergie. Offre une protection supérieure par rapport au générateur de bouclier compact.\n[c][00BB00]Résiste aux armes cinétiques et aux missiles, mais sensible aux lasers, au plasma et aux EMP.
Italiano: Un generatore di scudi standard progettato per offrire una protezione significativa contro impatti cinetici ed esplosivi, ma può essere interrotto da armi a energia. Offre una protezione superiore rispetto al generatore di scudi compatti.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste alle armi cinetiche e ai missili, ma è sensibile a laser, plasma ed EMP.
Spanish: Un generador de escudo estándar diseñado para ofrecer una protección significativa contra impactos cinéticos y explosivos, pero que puede ser interrumpido por armas basadas en energía. Ofrece una protección superior al generador de escudo compacto.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste armas cinéticas y misiles, pero es susceptible a láseres, plasma y EMP.
Chinese (simplified): 设计为能够提供良好动能及高爆抗性的标准护盾，但是会被能量武器干扰，可以提供远好于紧凑型护盾的防护效果\n[c][00BB00]可防御动能武器和导弹，难以抵御激光、等离子和电磁脉冲武器[-][/c]

English: A military-issue Shield Generator designed to offer superior protection against hostile attack over the Standard Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.\n[-][/c][66CCFF]Must be upgraded from the Standard Shield Generator using a Multitool.
Deutsch: Ein militärischer Schildgenerator, der überlegenen Schutz vor feindlichen Angriffen gegenüber dem Standard-Schildgenerator bietet.\n[c][00BB00]Widersteht kinetischen Waffen und Raketen, ist aber anfällig für Laser, Plasma und EMP.\n[-][/ c][66CCFF]Muss vom Standard-Schildgenerator mit einem Multitool aktualisiert werden.
Français: Un générateur de bouclier militaire conçu pour offrir une protection supérieure contre les attaques hostiles par rapport au générateur de bouclier standard.\n[c][00BB00]Résiste aux armes cinétiques et aux missiles, mais sensible aux lasers, au plasma et aux EMP.\n[-][/ c][66CCFF]Doit être mis à niveau à partir du générateur de bouclier standard à l'aide d'un multi-outil.
Italiano: Un generatore di scudi di emissione militare progettato per offrire una protezione superiore contro gli attacchi ostili rispetto al generatore di scudi standard.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste alle armi cinetiche e ai missili, ma è sensibile a laser, plasma ed EMP.\n[-][/ c][66CCFF]Deve essere aggiornato dal generatore di scudi standard utilizzando un multiutensile.
Spanish: Un generador de escudo militar diseñado para ofrecer una protección superior contra ataques hostiles sobre el generador de escudo estándar.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste armas cinéticas y misiles, pero es susceptible a láseres, plasma y EMP.\n[-][/ c][66CCFF]Debe actualizarse desde el Generador de escudos estándar con una multiherramienta.
Chinese (simplified): 一种军用护盾发生器，旨在提供比标准护盾发生器更高级的防护以抵御敌对攻击。\n[c][00BB00]抵御动能武器和导弹，但对激光、等离子和电磁脉冲敏感。[-][/c]

English: Unstable, supersatured polycrystal of Pentaxium. If placed in a hydroponics unit with a supply of mineral solution it will grow and form larger crystals of Pentaxid.\n[c][FF00FF]Radioactive and Volatile. Drains power from structure grid while growing.
Chinese (simplified): 不稳定的过饱和多晶型翘曲水晶，置于水培箱中并施以矿物溶液可以生长为更大的翘曲水晶晶体\n[c][FF00FF]具有放射性且易爆，生长时会从建筑中吸取能量[-][/c]

English: A Generator that operates by fusing two or more elements together to release massive amounts of energy.\nRequires a constant energy input to keep the reaction stable, making it suitable for high-output spacecrafts
Chinese (simplified): 一种通过将两个或更多元素融合在一起来释放大量能量的发电机。\n需要持续的能量输入以保持反应稳定，使其适合高输出的宇宙飞船。

English: You are dehydrated!\nReplenish your fluids by drinking water, juice or tea!
Deutsch: Sie sind dehydriert!\nFüllen Sie Ihre Flüssigkeit durch Wasser, Saft oder Tee wieder auf!
Français: Vous êtes déshydraté!\nFaites le plein en buvant de l'eau, du jus ou du thé!
Italiano: Sei disidratato!\nRifornisci i tuoi liquidi bevendo acqua, succhi di frutta o tè!
Spanish: ¡Estás deshidratado!\n¡Repone tus líquidos bebiendo agua, jugo o té!
Chinese (simplified): 你脱水了!\n快喝点水，果汁或是茶来补充水分!

English: You have been poisoned!\nThe poison has spread through your body and can only be treated with Antitoxic Pills, Injections or a Detox Kit
Deutsch: Sie wurden vergiftet!\nDas Gift hat sich in Ihrem Körper ausgebreitet und kann nur mit antitoxischen Pillen, Injektionen oder einem Detox-Kit behandelt werden
Français: Vous avez été empoisonné !\nLe poison s'est propagé dans votre corps et ne peut être traité qu'avec des pilules antitoxiques, des injections ou un kit de désintoxication
Italiano: Sei stato avvelenato!\nIl veleno si è diffuso nel tuo corpo e può essere trattato solo con pillole antitossiche, iniezioni o un kit disintossicante
Spanish: ¡Te han envenenado!\nEl veneno se ha esparcido por tu cuerpo y solo se puede tratar con píldoras antitóxicas, inyecciones o un kit de desintoxicación.
Chinese (simplified): 你中毒了！毒素已经遍布你的全身，只能用抗毒药片、注射剂或解毒医疗包来治疗。

English: A large auxillary capacitor bank used in larger vessels dedicated to supplying additional energy to a shield generator; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.
Chinese (simplified): 一个大型辅助电容器组，用于为护盾发生器提供额外的能量，以牺牲护盾充电速度为代价来增加护盾强度。

English: A primary capacitor that subsumes the role of a battleship's main power storage for shield generation; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.
Chinese (simplified): 一个主电容器，它承担了战斗舰主电源存储的作用，用于生成护盾；以护盾充电速度为代价增加护盾强度。

English: An auxillary power coupling with tremendous throughput that diverts higher charge to a shield generator; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.
Chinese (simplified): 一个具有巨大吞吐量的辅助电源耦合器，将更高的电荷转移到护盾发生器；以护盾强度为代价增加护盾充电速度。

English: The primary energy conduit outfitted with superconductors used for supplying power from a Battleship's generators to the shield capacitors; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.
Chinese (simplified): 主能量通道配备了超导体，用于从战舰的发电机向护盾电容器供应能量；以护盾强度为代价提高护盾充电速度。

English: You are suffering from Endo-Parasites. Use Anti-Parasite Pills, Anti-Parasite Injection or the Decontamination Kit!
Chinese (simplified): 你正受到内寄生虫的困扰。使用抗寄生虫药片、抗寄生虫注射剂或净化试剂盒！

English: Extra-Large structural armor blocks used to produce elongated armor shapes made of steel.
Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钢制的延长型护甲形状。

Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钛合金制的延长型护甲形状。

English: Extra-Large structural armor blocks used to produce elongated armor shapes made of Sathium Alloy.
Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钑合金制的延长型护甲形状。

Chinese (simplified): 由贸易联盟银行发行的高价值白金信用卡。每张信用卡代表可以在自动取款机存入的总计10,000信用点。\n大多数企业不接受白金信用卡。

English: A Type-22 Deployable Heavy Mechanoid for militarized structures.\nPlaces the Mechanoid's charging pad from which they will be deployed.\nWill patrol the area and engage hostile targets.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于军事化结构的22型可部署重型机械人。\n放置机械人的充电垫，他们将从这里被部署。\n将巡逻区域并与敌对目标交战。

Vietnamese: Cây không phát triển vì nhiệt độ quá cao hoặc quá thấp

English: [c][FFA500]Plant is not growing because there is not enough light[-][/c]\nPlace a grow light above.
Deutsch: Pflanze kann nicht wachsen da sie nicht genügend Licht bekommt
Français: Les plantes ne peuvent pas pousser car il n'y a pas assez de lumière
Italiano: La pianta non sta crescendo perchè non c'è abbastanza luce
Spanish: La planta no está creciendo porque no hay suficiente luz
Portuguese (Brazil): A vegetação não esta crescendo pois não há iluminação suficiente
Polish: Roślina nie może urosnąć ze względu na zbyt niskie nasłonecznienie
Japanese: 十分な光がないので, 植物は成長していない
Chinese (simplified): [c][FFA500]植物因为光线不足而不生长[-][/c]\n在上方放置植物生长灯。
Chinese (traditional): 植物沒有生長，因為光線不夠
Greek: Το φυτό δεν μεγαλώνει γιατί δεν υπάρχει αρκετό φως
Vietnamese: Cây không phát triển vì không có đủ ánh sáng

English: [c][FFA500]Plant is not growing because there is no oxygen[-][/c]\nMake sure room is airtight and supply oxygen via ventilators.
Deutsch: Pflanze kann auf Grund von fehlender Atmosphäre nicht wachsen
Français: Les plantes ne peuvent pas pousser car il n'y a pas d'oxygène
Italiano: La pianta non sta crescendo perchè non c'è ossigeno
Spanish: La planta no está creciendo porque no hay oxígeno
Portuguese (Brazil): A vegetação não esta crescendo pois não há oxygênio suficiente
Polish: Roślina nie może urosnąć ze względu na zbyt niski poziom tlenu
Japanese: 酸素がないので, 植物は成長していない
Chinese (simplified): 植物没有生长，因为没有氧气
Chinese (traditional): 植物沒有生長，因為沒有氧氣
Greek: Το φυτό δεν μεγαλώνει γιατί δεν υπάρχει οξυγόνο
Vietnamese: Cây không phát triển vì không có oxy

English: You cannot damage the target with this weapon!\nWeapon is not powerful enough or structure is protected by an [c][00ffff]admin core[-][/c].
Deutsch: Mit dieser Waffe kannst du dein Ziel nicht beschädigen!\nSchalte per RMT in einen anderen Modus oder wähle eine andere Waffe.
Français: Cette arme n'a aucune incidence sur la cible! \nPassez sur un autre mode d'arme avec «clic Droit» ou utilisez une autre arme.
Italiano: Non puoi danneggiare il bersaglio con questa arma!\nCambia modalità di fuoco o arma.
Spanish: ¡No puedes dañar al objetivo con esta arma!\nCambia a un modo de arma diferente con BDR o usa otra arma.
Portuguese (Brazil): Você não pode danificar o alvo com esta arma!\nMude para um modo de arma diferente clicando em BtnDir ou use outra arma.
Polish: Nie możesz uszkodzić celu za pomocą tej broni! Przełącz tryb strzelania za pomocą PPM lub użyj innej broni.
Russian: Вы не можете повредить цель этим оружием!\nПереключите режим стрельбы при помощи ПКМ или используйте другое оружие.
Japanese: この武器でターゲットにダメージを与えることはできません!\nRMBをクリックして別の武器モードに切り替えるか, 別の武器を使用してください.
Chinese (simplified): 你无法用该武器伤害目标!\n可能是武器不够强大，又或者是该结构受到到 [c][00ffff]管理员核心[-][/c]保护.
Chinese (traditional): 此武器無效！ \n使用其他武器，或者單擊鼠標右鍵切換到不同的武器模式。
Greek: Δεν μπορείς να κάνεις ζημιά σε αυτόν τον στόχο με αυτό το όπλο!\nΆλλαξε το όπλο σε μία διαφορετική λειτουργία πατώντας Δεξί Κλικ ή χρησιμοποίησε ένα άλλο όπλο.
Vietnamese: Bạn không thể gây sát thương mục tiêu bằng vũ khí này!\n Chuyển sang chế độ vũ khí khác bằng cách nhấp vào RMB hoặc sử dụng vũ khí khác.

English: You are playing the [c][00ffff]Reforged Eden[-][/c] scenario. Please see the Reforged Eden workshop or contact your server admin for support!
Deutsch: Bitte beachten: Der Überlebenskonstruktor kann nur Gegenstände aus dem INVENTAR verwenden (nicht aber aus dem Schnellzugriff)
Français: A noter que le Constructeur de survie utilise seulement les éléments de l'INVENTAIRE (pas de la barre outils).
Italiano: Attenzione: Il Costruttore di Sopravvivenza può utilizzare solo gli oggetti dell'Inventario (non funziona con la Barra degli Strumenti)
Spanish: Nota: El Constructor de Supervivencia sólo puede utilizar objetos del INVENTARIO (pero no de la Barra de Herramientas)
Portuguese (Brazil): Por favor note: O Construtor de Sobrevivência só pode usar itens do INVENTÁRIO (mas não da Barra de Ferramentas)
Polish: Informacja: Podręczny konstruktor może korzystać tylko z przedmiotów w INWENTARZU (ale nie z paska narzędzi)
Russian: Будьте внимательны: Встроенный конструктор может использовать предметы только из инвентаря (панель инструментов для него не доступна)
Japanese: 注意:サバイバルコンストラクタはインベントリーのアイテムのみを使用できます(ツールバーからは使用できません)
Chinese (simplified): 您正在玩[c][00ffff]重铸伊甸园[-][/c]剧本。请查看重铸伊甸园工坊或联系您的服务器管理员以获取支持！
Chinese (traditional): 請注意:生存建造機只能使用背包中的物品 (不能使用快捷欄的物品)
Greek: Σημείωσε ότι: Ο Κατασκευαστής Επιβίωσης μπορεί μόνο να χρησιμοποιηθεί από το INVENTORY σου (αλλά όχι από την Γραμμή Εργαλειών)
Dutch: Notitie: De overlevings constructeur kan enkel items uit de inventaris gebruiken (en niet uit de Toolbar)
Vietnamese: Xin lưu ý: Chế tạo sinh tồn chỉ có thể sử dụng các mục từ túi đồ chứ không phải từ Thanh công cụ)

Japanese: ストレージがありません

English:
[c][00ffff]>>>Read the PDA First[-][/c] [sup][c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c][/sup][c][00ffff]<<<[-][/c][sup]

[c][00ffff]Missions:[-][/c] Missions are managed under the Solo Missions tab. Start completing the Reforged Galaxy or Project Eden story missions to unlock additional missions.
[c][00ffff]Empyriopedia:[-][/c] Contains a comprehensive encyclopedia of the scenario and can answer many of your questions. Additional entries are unlocked as you progress through the scenario.
[c][00ffff]Journey Book:[-][/c] Shows a log of previous mission dialog.

[c][00ffff]Tooltips:[-][/c] Tooltips provide important information on many items and devices. Mouse over any item in your inventory, constructor, or tech tree to view details.

[c][00ffff]Planets and Sectors:[-][/c] Planets and sectors in the current solar system are scanned and a basic description of each can be viewed on the local or solar system map.

[c][00ffff]Galaxy:[-][/c] Project Eden contains a large galaxy viewable on the galaxy map. Star class and faction territory change what you may find in a star system.

[c][00ffff]Mass, Volume and CPU:[-][/c] The mass, volume, and CPU restrictions are enabled by default. Use the logistics system to move items too large to fit in the player inventory.

[c][00ffff]Escaping your starting system:[-][/c] Resources to build a basic small vessel can be found on your starting planet.
Resources for a warp capable small vessel can be found on the moon of your starting planet.
Resources for a warp capable capital vessel are on other planets in your starting solar system.
Advanced resources are found in other star systems.[/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][00ffff]>>>首先阅读PDA[-][/c] [sup][c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c][/sup][c][00ffff]<<<[-][/c][sup]

[c][00ffff]任务:[-][/c] 任务在单独任务标签下管理。开始完成重制银河系或伊甸园项目故事任务，以解锁额外任务。
[c][00ffff]百科全书:[-][/c] 包含场景的综合百科全书，可以回答许多问题。随着你在场景中的进展，额外的条目会被解锁。
[c][00ffff]旅程书:[-][/c] 显示前一个任务对话的日志。

[c][00ffff]工具提示:[-][/c] 工具提示提供了许多物品和设备的重要信息。将鼠标悬停在你库存、构造器或科技树中的任何物品上，以查看详细信息。

[c][00ffff]星球和区域:[-][/c] 扫描当前太阳系的星球和区域，可以在本地或太阳系地图上查看每个星球的基本描述。

[c][00ffff]星系:[-][/c] 伊甸园项目包含一个可以在星系地图上看到的大型星系。星类和派系领土会改变你在星系中的发现。

[c][00ffff]质量、体积和CPU:[-][/c] 默认情况下，质量、体积和CPU限制是启用的。使用后勤系统移动太大而无法放入玩家库存的物品。

[c][00ffff]逃离你的起始系统:[-][/c] 在你的起始星球上可以找到建造基础小型飞船的资源。在起始星球的月球上可以找到用于翘曲的小型飞船的资源。在起始太阳系的其它星球上可以找到用于翘曲的大型飞船的资源。在其他星系中可以找到高级资源。[/sup]

English: The Drone Swarm is a deadly menace.
Chinese (simplified): 无人机群是一个致命的威胁。

English: Alien drones of unknown origin. Hostile.
Chinese (simplified): 未知来源的外星无人机。敌对的。

English: A geothermal generator usable on planets with high geological activity. Reduces the power usage of your base while active.\nInteract with the geothermal generator after placement to begin the activation process. Requires unlocking Active Geothermal Generator in the tech tree.
Chinese (simplified): 一种可用于地质活动频繁的星球上的地热发电机。在活动时减少您基地的电力使用。放置后与地热发电机互动以开始激活过程。需要在科技树中解锁活动地热发电机。

English: Active geothermal generators reduce the power usage of your base.\nRequires activating a geothermal generator using a geological core sample.\nBase will still require a standard generator and fuel tank to run.
Chinese (simplified): 主动地热发电机可以降低你的基地的电力使用。\n需要使用地质核心样本激活地热发电机。\n基地仍然需要一个标准发电机和燃料罐来运行。

English:
For the large scale extraction of resources from water.
[c][00ffff]Requires a specific activation process.[-][/c][sup]

[c][00FFFF][b]Requirements:[/b][-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Must be placed on a base within logistics range of the [b]Lake[/b] (internal name Water) biome.
-Interact with the extractor to begin the activation process.
-Requires 1 Small Optronic Matrix to activate.
Multiple extractors can be linked together in a network.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]Requires schematic purchased from Free Colonists or found as loot. Requires level 15 to craft and level 20 to activate.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
用于大规模提取水中资源.
[c][00ffff]需要以特定方式激活.[-][/c][sup]

[c][00FFFF][b]需求:[/b][-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-所在的基地物流网络必须能够覆盖 [b]湖泊[/b] (内部代码为Water) 生物群系.
-与提取器互动以启动激活程序.
-启动需要消耗1个小光电矩阵.
多个提取器可以链接为一个网络.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]需要从殖民者处购买蓝图或作为战利品搜刮得到. 制造需要15级，启动需要20级.[-][/c]

English: For the large scale extraction of resources from water. This extractor is acting as the primary extractor. Additional extractors may be networked together.
Chinese (simplified): 用于大规模从水中提取资源。这台提取器是主要的提取器。额外的提取器可能会联网在一起。

English:
A block for POIs. Can be salvaged or deconstructed for components.

[FFFF00]This block cannot be used by players. Installation onto a player base or ship may overload the CPU systems and cause damage.[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个用于POI的方块。可以被打捞或拆解为组件。

[c][FFFF00]这个方块不能被玩家使用。安装到玩家基地或船上可能会使CPU系统过载并造成损害。[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]需要Project Eden或Reforged Eden。[/i][-][/c]

English: [c][A9A9A9]This item is from Reforged Eden and has no use in Project Eden. It is included for compatibility reasons.\nPlease do not report.\nThis item will automatically decay on its own or it may be trashed.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [c][A9A9A9]这玩意只有RE才有，PE里不存在. 之所以在这是因为要兼容点什么.\n请不要进行相关的bug上报.\n这东西自己会烂掉.[-][/c]

English: A data pad containing information on the Andromeda galaxy.\n\nTurn in at the Research Computer on board UCH Research Vessels to obtain additional unlock points.
Chinese (simplified): 含有本星系各种信息的数据平板.\n\n在UCH船舰的研究计算机处上交以获得额外的解锁点数

English:
[c][ffffff]Upgrades:[-][/c] Capital Vessel Warp Drive
[c][ffffff]Base Range Increase:[-][/c] 1 Light Year
[c][ffffff]Max Upgrades:[-][/c] 50[c]

A data pad containing navigational data on the Andromeda galaxy. Allows you to plot safer and more efficient warp jumps.
Increases the maximum range you can warp while piloting any ship.

Turn in to Research Computers on UCH Research Vessels to increase the base range you can plot a warp jump.

[c][ffffff]升级:[-][/c] 主力舰翘曲驱动器

增加驾驶飞船时的最大跳跃距离.

在UCH船舰的研究计算机处上交以增加你的基础跳跃距离

English: This item is not currently used but may have a use in a future update. Hold on to it!
Chinese (simplified): 该物品目前还没有任何用途，未来的某次更新中会用到

English:
This license allows use of the furnaces on board [c][FFA500]Polaris orbital refineries.[/c][-] 

[c][FFFFFF][i]Place ores in the furnace input cargo container in the upper hangar. 
Pick up refined ingots from the bottom hangar.[/i]

这张许可证可以让你使用船上的熔炉[c][FFA500]极星轨道精炼厂[-][/c]。 

[c][FFFFFF][i]在机库上方的输入箱中放入矿石.

English:
A block group for placing Project Eden POI blocks in creative mode. RMB to change type. Not allowed in blueprints.

[c][FFFF00]THESE BLOCKS ARE ONLY FOR INTERNAL USE IN CREATIVE MODE BY THE SCENARIO DEVELOPER AND ARE NOT INTENDED FOR USE IN SURVIVAL.[-][/c]

一组用于在创造模式中放置的伊甸园计划方块. 右键以改变类型. 不允许出现在蓝图中.

[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A low powered generator for use on alien POIs. Not targeted by turrets.
Chinese (simplified): 外星POI使用的低功率发电机，无法被炮台锁定。

English:
A block group for placing Project Eden 2 dummy POI blocks in creative mode for upcoming RE2 compatibility. RMB to change type. Not allowed in blueprints.

[c][FFFF00]THESE BLOCKS ARE ONLY FOR INTERNAL USE IN CREATIVE MODE BY THE SCENARIO DEVELOPER AND ARE NOT INTENDED FOR USE IN SURVIVAL.[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

一组用于在兼容即将到来的RE2，在创造模式中放置的伊甸园计划假方块. 右键以改变类型. 不允许出现在蓝图中.

[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English:
A block group for placing various lifts. RMB to expand block selection group.
Lifts can be controlled via signals. Two switches or buttons tied to an XOR signal works well.
Lifts can only be directly interacted with via the corner frames on the very top and the platform does not block projectiles.
Not airtight. See individual tooltips for details.

[c][FFFF00]Experimental, may have issues, please leave feedback.[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一组多种型号的升降机方块. 右键展开方块选择.
升降机可以通过信号进行控制. 用XOR逻辑门连起来的两个开关效果就很好.
升降机可以互动的位置只有边缘的框架和最顶端，且平台不能阻挡投射物.
不气密. 参见每个方块单独的说明.

[c][FFFF00]实验性，可能造成问题，请留下反馈.[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A small lift for interior use. Other blocks can be placed within the lower parts of the lift bounding box.
Chinese (simplified): 室内用的小升降机，别的方块可以放在升降机下半部分的边界框内

English: A small lift without a frame for interior use. Other blocks can be placed within the lower parts of the lift bounding box. To interact with the lift you must use the keypad on the very top of the lift.
Chinese (simplified): 一个室内用的无框小升降机. 别的方块可以放在升降机下半部分的边界框内. 与电梯互动则必须使用顶上的面板.

English: A large lift that uses micro tractor beams to raise and lower the platform. Requires adding shutter doors or forcefields to maintain airtightness.
Chinese (simplified): 一个利用微型牵引光束来控制平台的升降机. 需要安装门或是力场来保持气密.

English:
A high powered vulcan turret. Best used with manual control. Can switch between a medium range and short range mode with right click while under manual control. 
Short range mode uses up ammo fast. 
[c][FFFFFF]Schematic required to unlock.[-][/c] 

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一门强力的火神炮塔，手操时效果最好，可以按下右键切换中距和近距模式 
近距模式弹药消耗非常高. 
[c][FFFFFF]通过蓝图解锁.[-][/c] 

[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]
阿比赛尔等离子护盾发生器

English: An invisible block for controlling decals. Has 1 hp so easily destroyed with explosions. Invisible model so it can be placed near a core or fuel tanks. When destroyed or removed it will disable the decals it controls as set in the control panel.
Chinese (simplified): 一个用于控制贴花的隐形方块，只有1生命所以很容易会被爆炸破坏，模型是看不见的所以说可以放在油箱或核心边上，一旦被破坏它就会关闭在控制面板中指定的贴花

English: A dummy control block for use in unarmed orbital patrol vessels that enables them to receive patrol orders. Acts as a turret. This device should remain OFF at all times. POI use only.
Chinese (simplified): 用于无武装轨道巡逻舰的虚拟控制方块，使它们能够接收巡逻命令。效果类似于炮台。该设备应始终保持关闭状态。仅供 POI 使用。

English: A heavy damage vulcan turret. \n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一门高伤害的火神炮塔. \n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A block to increase the shield capacity or recharge rate of Project Eden POIs. Gives back a Combat Steel block when salvaged.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个用于增加伊甸园项目POIs的护盾容量或充能速率的方块。回收时会返还一个战斗钢方块。

English: A long range turret that fires a fast moving projectile.\n[c][00FF00]Alternate fire modes available via right click.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一门可以发射高速投射物的远程炮塔\n[c][00FF00]右键可切换次要开火模式.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: Ammunition for the Light Railgun Turret.

A long range turret that fires a fast moving projectile for high damage especially to armor.Uses a high amount of power while active. 50% more dps than the Light Railgun Turret at the cost of reduced tracking.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一门可以发射高速投射物的远程炮塔，启动时需要消耗大量电力，更低的瞄准速度换来了比轻型版本高出50%的DPS\n[c][FFFFFF]通过蓝图解锁.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: Ammunition for the Heavy Railgun Turret.

A close range flak turret of UCH design capable of dealing heavy and consistent damage to drones and fighters but lacks the ability to deal significant damage to armor or devices.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种基于UCH设计的短距炮塔，能够给对迫近的无人机和战斗机持续造成猛烈的伤害，但是对装甲和机载设备较为乏力\n[c][FFFFFF]通过蓝图解锁.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: Ammunition for the Sentinel Flak Turret.

A reinforced cargo container for POIs and NPC ships.

Very high HP to survive most battles. Set loot via container ID in the control panel.
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种用于POI和NPC飞船的强化货箱

非常高的血量使其可以在战斗之后依然完整，在控制面板用利用Container ID来设定其中的战利品
[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English:
Wreckage that can be salvaged or deconstructed for raw materials or sold to Free Colonists Scrapyards.

Sometimes leaves behind a box with valuable materials when removed from wrecks.

Most often found in orbital wreckage.
Chinese (simplified):
可以分解为原材料或者售卖给自由殖民者的残骸.

从残骸中移出时偶尔会留下一个装有高价值材料的容器.

多见于轨道残骸.

English: A decorative block for POIs. Dialog enabled. \n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 用于POI的装饰方块. 已启用对话. \n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A subspace radio that transmits audio on all frequencies. Can be shot at to remove, or deactivated in the control panel.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种亚空间无线电，能够在所有频率上传输音频。可以射击以移除，或在控制面板中停用。
亚空间无线电 (自由殖民者)
亚空间无线电 (无人机蜂群)

English: A decorative laser beam for POIs. Can remove via multitool by aiming at the block base, or can be turned off in the control panel.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 用于POI的装饰性激光束。可以通过瞄准块基的多工具移除，也可以在控制面板中关闭。\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园项目或重铸伊甸园。[/i][-][/c]

English: A heavily armored decoy for POIs that sends out false sensor readings to fool enemy turrets to fire on it.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种为POIs设计的重型装甲诱饵，它发出虚假的传感器读数，诱使敌人炮塔向其开火。\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园计划。[/i][-][/c]
翘曲水晶小行星 (已宣誓主权)
富冰小行星 (已宣誓主权)
重冰小行星 (已宣誓主权)
[c][D2AF00][b]干扰过多 - 小行星扫描无法确定结果[/b][-][/c]
小型调制脉冲激光炮 [c][FF0000](红外)[-][/c]

English:
A modulated pulse laser that is capable of having its frequency crystal changed to adapt to different combat situations. 
Change frequency with the upgrade or downgrade function of a multitool.

See the associated frequency cell for stats.

English:
A fixed mining laser for mining dense and rich ice asteroids found in special sites.
This ice mining laser is specially modulated to only mine dense and rich ice asteroids and will not work on any other material.
Focus on a target ice asteroid until it is depleted, it can take some time and take some fiddling depending on the number of lasers being used.

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种固定采矿激光器，用于开采在特殊地点发现的密集且富饶的冰质小行星。

聚焦目标冰质小行星，直到它被耗尽，这可能需要一些时间，并且根据使用的激光器数量可能需要一些调整。
[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园项目或重铸伊甸园。[/i][-][/c]

Can aim straight up but cannot aim down.\nConfigure target settings in the control panel.\nUse sparingly as audio from multiple alarms can overlap. Recommended to assign to a shortcut on the control panel for easy toggling.
Chinese (simplified): 一个预警系统，在哨兵警报前方的范围内和视线内探测到威胁时提供声音警告。它的工作原理与炮塔相同，具有相同的限制和要求。可以直指向上，但不能向下瞄准。\n在控制面板中配置目标设置。\n由于多个警报的声音可能会重叠，请谨慎使用。建议在控制面板上分配一个快捷方式，以便于轻松切换。

English: An organic turret for Project Eden POIs.
Chinese (simplified): 用于伊甸园计划POI的有机体炮台

English: A turret for POIs that will restore the shield capacitor of the target.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于POIs的炮台，它将恢复目标的护盾电容器。

English:
A plasma cannon of Farr design.
Can be recharged from the Archivist in the Farr Archives on Parthix for a fee of 100,000 credits.

[c][A9A9A9][i]Do unto others.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一门Farr设计的等离子加农炮
可以在Farr母星的档案管理员处以100，000的价格重新充能.

[c][A9A9A9][i]己所不欲，勿施于人.[/i][-][/c]

English: This ammunition is recharged by the Brotherhood of Farr.
Chinese (simplified): 该弹药只能由Farr兄弟会人员充能

English: A long range and highly accurate but slow firing missile launcher.\nThis launcher is configured to fire explosive warheads dealing heavy damage to armor and devices and light damage to shields.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种低射速的远程高精度导弹\n该发射器被设定为发射高爆弹头，会对方块和设备造成非常高的伤害，但对护盾伤害非常有限.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A long range tactical missile used in Cruise Missile Launchers. Armed with an explosive warhead for increased hull and device damage.
Chinese (simplified): 一枚用于巡航导弹发射器的远程战术导弹，其携带的高爆弹头能对方块和设备造成大量伤害
电磁脉冲巡航导弹发射器

English: A long range and highly accurate but slow firing missile launcher.\nThis launcher is configured to fire EMP warheads dealing heavy damage to shields and minimal damage to armor and devices.\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

电磁脉冲巡航导弹发射器

English: A long range tactical missile used in Cruise Missile Launchers. Armed with a EMP warhead for increased shield damage.
Chinese (simplified): 一枚用于巡航导弹发射器的远程战术导弹，其携带的电磁脉冲弹头能对护盾造成大量伤害

English: Fires multiple highly accurate smart missiles at the target.\n[c][FFFF00]AI control only.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

蜂群发射器所使用的弹药

English: Projects a powerful beam of thermal energy burning away devices and hull. Requires an extreme amount of energy to be active. Has a reduced effect against heavy armor.\n[c][FFFF00]AI control only.[-][/c]\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
