English:
A station used for the launching of probes and scanning for various anomalies.

Used for science and scanning missions. Available scanning missions will appear under the Science and Scanning section in the PDA when you are in a sector that can be scanned and can be started either in the PDA or by accessing this device.
Accessing this device without an available mission does nothing.

[c][FFFF00]Do not place items into the inventory of this device.[-][/c]
NOTICE: THIS DEVICE IS UNDERGOING TESTING AND MAY NOT WORK AS EXPECTED.
Chinese (simplified):
一个用来发射探针以探测异常的工作站.

用于科学及扫描任务. 当你处于一个可扫描星区时，可用任务会显示在PDA的科学与扫描一栏中，你可以通过访问该设备或是PDA来进行任务.
没有可用任务时访问不会有任何效果.

[c][FFFF00]不要将物品置于该设备的库存中.[-][/c]
注意: 该物品仍处于测试状态且功能还不正常

English: An all-in-one research computer for managing expeditions, bounties, scientific research, opening reward caches, and other tasks.\n\nCurrently a work in progress.
Chinese (simplified): 一体化的研究计算机，可以用于管理远征，赏金，特定的研究，开启奖励箱子以及更多其他功能.\n\n仍处于开发中状态.

English:
A specialized reusable core for claiming a wreck or structure for salvage.
Placing this core will automatically power down the structure to prevent generator overload.
The core can be picked back up intact with [c][FFFF00]F[-] (default hot key) for use on other structures.
[sup][c][ffff00]Placing a core on a POI will permanently disable NPC dialogue on that POI. Do not place cores on mission POIs unless you have completed the mission objectives.[-][/c][/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
一种专用于占据残骸或其他结构以方便拆卸的核心
安装该核心会自动断电以防止过载.
核心可以通过按下 [c][FFFF00]F(默认) [-][/c]来拾起从而用于其他结构.
[sup][c][ffff00]在POI上使用该核心将永久禁用该建筑的NPC对话功能. 因此在你完成任务之前不要把该核心放置于任务POI上.[-][/c][/sup]

English:
A turret for POIs. Can be salvaged or deconstructed for components.

[FFFF00]This device cannot be used by players. Installation onto a player base or ship will overload the CPU systems.[-][/c]
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

English:
Allows the construction of various Drone Swarm enhanced Auxiliary CPU cores. Due to the alien nature of the technology and the danger of the Drone AI going rogue, you can have no more than 10 Auxiliary cores of any type installed on the same structure at a time.
Available cores are a CPU upgrade, a shield upgrade, and an energy upgrade.

Right Mouse to select device.

Shared Block Limit Category: [c][FF9A01]Auxiliary Cores[-][/c]

可用版本有CPU升级， a 护盾升级以及能量升级.

右键以访问选项.

English: Reflects holographic projections off magnetized nanoparticles to give the illusion of a flame. 特效投影仪 (蓝色引擎尾迹)

English: Leaves behind a thin stream of nanoparticles to give the illusion of an engine trail.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 在后方留下一道细小的纳米粒子流，给人一种发动机尾迹的错觉。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (红色引擎尾迹)

English: Creates an ionized channel that conducts electricity through it.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 创造一条电力可以流通的电离管路。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]

English: Reflects holographic projections off clumps of nanoparticles to give the illusion of fireflies.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 利用纳米颗粒团块反射全息投影，产生萤火虫的幻象。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (指引环 蓝色)

English:
Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a strong holograpic projection off of them to create a large ring of lights to act as a docking guide for space stations. The ring is several hundred meters in diameter.
Place in the center of your space station.

[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射出高亮度的全息投影，从而形成一个大的光环，作为空间站的对接指引. 环有数百米大.
置于空间站中心.

[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (指引 蓝色)

English: Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a strong holograpic projection off of them to create a line of static docking guides outward from the emitter.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射出高亮度的全息投影，从而形成由发射器向外的一排静态对接引导线。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
效果投影仪 (指引 橙色)
效果投影仪 (指引 青色 动画)

English:
Arranged nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a rotating holograpic projection off of them to project a line of animated docking guides outward from the emitter.
These projections are offset slightly to match up seamlessly when placed next to a static docking guide.

[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射它们的旋转全息投影，从而由发射器向外投射一条可动对接引导线.
当放置在静态对接导轨旁边时，这些投影会稍微偏移以保证无缝.

[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
效果投影仪(引导黄色动画)

English: A decorative block fitting the season! This block's appearance will change throughout the year.\n\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

English: A decorative prop for your head fit for the season! This item's appearance will change throughout the year.
Chinese (simplified): 一个可以立在你头上的季节性装饰!  这个方块在一年中不同的时候会有不同的外观

English: A heavy plasma cannon carried by the most elite royal guards of the Zirax Empire. The weapon has a magnetic guidance system that allows the plasma projectiles to home in on the target.\nFinding ammunition for this weapon may be quite difficult.
Chinese (simplified): 由兹瑞克斯帝国最为精锐的皇家卫队所携带的重型等离子加农炮. 该武器拥有磁性导引系统，使其可以跟踪目标.\n获取这种武器的弹药可能会很困难.

English: Ammunition for the Royal Plasma Cannon. One cartridge refills the entire clip.
Chinese (simplified): 皇家等离子炮的弹药。一发弹夹可完全重新装填。

A dual picture decorative poster for hanging on your wall.

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]

English: A supporting structure required for wind turbines. Must be placed outdoors and elevated off the ground by at least 1 supporting block. Place a Wind Turbine directly on top.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Wind Turbines take up a 5x5 space.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 用于支撑风力发电机的支撑结构. 必须放置在室外且高于地面1个支撑方块或以上. 直接将风力发电机放置于上方.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]风力发电机需要占用 5x5 的空间.[-][/c]

English:
A wind turbine that reduces power consumption by [c][00FF00]300W[-][/c] [c][abd1ff]once activated.
If below requirements are met the turbine will spin up over 60 seconds and then become[-][/c] [c][00FF00]permanently active.[-][/c]

[c][00FFFF][b]Requirements:[/b][-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Outdoors with no obstructions above.
-Placed on top of a wind turbine base.
-Temperature 15C to 35C (60F to 95F).
-Radiation less than 0.4 rad.
-Breathable atmosphere.
-If it gives a 'not enough light warning' raise the turbine base higher off the ground.[-][/c][/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
一旦开启，风力发电机可以降低 [c][00FF00]75W[-][/c] [c][abd1ff]的能耗.
如果达成以下条件，风力发电机就会开始运作，并在60秒后变为[-][/c] [c][00FF00]永久开启.[-][/c]

[c][00FFFF][b]条件:[/b][-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]-户外，上方没有阻挡物.
-放置在风力发电机基座上方.
-温度在 15C 到 35C (60F to 95F)之间.
-辐射低于0.4.
-可呼吸的大气.
-如果出现 '光照不足' 的警告，就把基座垫高一些.[-][/c]

English:
A wind turbine designed for passive power generation on planets. Must be placed directly on top of a Wind Turbine Base.
It will spin up over 1 minute then if conditions are favorable it will provide a passive reduction in power consumption to your structure until it is removed.
Requires another source of power before it can activate.
Can not activate in extreme heat, cold, radiation, or where there is not a breathable atmosphere.
Chinese (simplified):
风力发电机被设计为用于在星球上持续获取电力. 必须被直接放置在风力发电机基座上方.
如果条件合适，它将花费一分钟来启动，并在被拆除前一直被动为建筑降低能耗.
启动时需要其他电源.
无法在极高/低温，辐射或是无法呼吸的环境中使用.

English: This wind turbine is reducing the power consumption of your structure. It will continue to operate until it is removed.
Chinese (simplified): 该风力发电机正在为建筑降低能耗，并会在被拆除前一直保持运作。

English:
A significant upgrade to wind turbines that reduces power consumption by [c][00FF00]600W.[-][/c]
[c][abd1ff]Cannot be crafted in a constructor. Only 15 advanced wind turbines can be upgraded per base. Upgrade existing active turbines with a multitool.
Cannot upgrade idle wind turbines.[-][/c]
[c][FFFF00]Advanced Wind Turbines should be downgraded with a multitool before removing to prevent loss of components.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种大幅升级的风力发电机，可以降低 [c][00FF00]600W[-][/c]的能耗
[c][abd1ff]无法在建造机中建造。 每个基地只能升级15个风力发电机. 用多功能建造枪进行升级.
未启动的风力发电机无法升级.[-][/c]
[c][FFFF00]拆除先进风力发电机之前最好先进行降级以防丢失部分组件.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]使用设计图来解锁.[-][/c]

English: An empty hydroponics bay for planting specialized crops. \nAdd sprouts in an advanced constructor then place on top of a single growing plot. Requires a single grow lamp placed directly above. \nDoes not protect crops from environmental hazards.
Chinese (simplified): 可用于培育特定作物的空水培箱\n使用高级建造机来加入幼苗. 置于单个生长箱上方，并在正上方放置一个植物生长射灯即可开始生长. \n无法抵挡环境灾害

English: A hydroponics bay for growing specialized crops. Place on top of a single growing plot. Requires a single grow lamp placed directly above. \nDoes not protect crops from environmental hazards.
Chinese (simplified): 可用于培育特定作物的水培箱\n 置于单个生长箱上方，并在正上方放置一个植物生长射灯即可开始生长. \n无法抵挡环境灾害

English: Hydroponics Bay (Natural Stimulant) Ready for Harvest

English: Hydroponics Bay (Herbal Leaves) Ready for Harvest

English: Hydroponics Bay (Plant Protein) Ready for Harvest

English:
Place on a planetary resource deposit to automatically mine it over time.
Requires special Industrial Fuel to be inserted into the fuel slots at the top of its inventory.
Has a lower yield per hour but much greater fuel and storage capacity than standard auto mining devices.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
置于矿床上方便可根据时间推移获取矿物.
需要消耗特殊的工业燃料包.
产率相对常规自动采矿机较低，但燃料容量和矿物储量都大大增加了.
[c][FFFFFF]通过原理图解锁。[-][/c]

English: Occasionally while mining certain deposits or asteroids you will obtain a whole piece of ore. These serve no purpose and can be trashed. This is due to a technical reason.
Chinese (simplified): 在手动挖掘时偶尔会挖出来一个矿物方块，这东西的出现是因为技术原因并且没有任何实际作用，可以直接销毁
虚空物质碎片\n[c][ff0000](需要虚空物质采集器)[-][/c]
虚空物质结晶\n[c][ff0000](需要先进虚空物质采集器)[-][/c]

English: The purification process of this ore requires water.
Chinese (simplified): 这种矿物的提纯需要用到水

English: A fine powder of highly processed silver.
Chinese (simplified): 深度加工过的细腻银粉

English: Hardened rock that cannot be removed.\n\n[c][ff0000]Internal scenario developer use only.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 无法移除的硬化岩石.\n\n[c][ff0000]场景开发者内部使用.[-][/c]

English:
An iron oxide ore commonly found in Hematite asteroids.

Certain individuals and mining corporations may be interested in this but it's not used in any known constructor recipes or commonly traded for.

Can be packaged into an Ore Shipment in the Decoration tab of your constructor for use in mining missions.

Used in Tier 1 mining missions.

某些个体和公司可能会对这种矿物感兴趣，但是目前无法用于制造或是交易.

可以在建造机的装饰一栏中制造为矿物包裹，用于完成采矿任务.

用于1级采矿任务

English: A survey report on various spacial anomalies, wrecks, or other objects of interest. UCH Research Vessels may be interested in this.

English: A survey report of asteroids, gasses, and interstellar dust. Mining Foremen on deep space mining vessels may be interested in this.
Chinese (simplified): 小行星、气体和星际尘埃的调查报告。 深空采矿船上的采矿工头可能对此感兴趣。

English: A survey report of wrecks, weapon signatures, and subspace communications. Bounty hunter offices may be interested in this.
Chinese (simplified): 残骸、武器特征和亚空间通信的调查报告。 赏金猎人办公室可能对此感兴趣。

English: Used to activate a geothermal generator on a planet with high geological activity.\nPlace in a connected container and use the upgrade function of a multitool on a geothermal generator to activate it.\nThe core sample is too heavy to lift via ship and will quickly cool into a pile of unusable stone.
Chinese (simplified): 用于在多地质活动的行星上激活地热发电机.\n放入连接的容器中并用多功能工具枪的升级功能来激活地热发电机.\n岩芯样本实在是太重以至于无法用飞船运输，且会很快冷却成一堆无法没有卵用的石头.

English: Salvaged part from an alien Drone used in the construction of computational devices.
Chinese (simplified): 从外星无人机上打捞到的部件，用于制造计算设备

English: A very rare AI core from an alien Drone used in the construction of advanced devices.
Chinese (simplified): 一颗从外星无人机上打捞到的极其稀有的AI核心，用于高端设备制造

Time reduction: [c][FFFFFF]30 minutes[-][/c]

只能被用于仍缺失组件的蓝图.

[c][D5D5D5]Savanth has been a thorn in the side of the Free Colonists for a number of years. Responsible for a number of bandit attacks on shipping lanes, he has now stepped up his attacks to include stations and civilian outposts.
The Free Colonists will pay for proof of his demise, although it is often not long until he returns in a freshly cloned body.[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF][b]通缉方:[/b][-][/c] [c][4CA5FF]自由殖民者(Free Colonists)[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF][b]隶属于:[/b][-][/c] [c][BF0000]强盗(Bandits)[-][/c]
将其带到殖民者领土内交易站区的赏金猎人办公室领取奖励。

[c][D5D5D5]萨万斯多年来一直是自由殖民者(Free Colonists)的眼中钉。他负责多次针对航运路线的强盗(Bandits)袭击，现在他的袭击已经升级，包括对站点和平民前哨的攻击。
自由殖民者(Free Colonists)将为他的死亡证据支付报酬，尽管他经常不久就会在一个新克隆的身体中回来。[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]Suspected of being a terrorist leader in the pirate gang known as the Bloodhunters, Marko made a name for himself for his extreme tactics.
He is wanted for his involvement in the asteroid bombardment of Intrazia Prime.[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]怀疑是被称为血猎者的海盗团伙中的恐怖主义领袖，马克以他的极端战术而声名狼藉。
他因参与对Intrazia Prime的小行星轰炸而遭到通缉。[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]Small Tony runs a local bandit gang and has frequently been spotted hiding out in derelict space stations.
Thought to have been killed more often than any other bandit, he keeps coming back for more thanks to his clone chamber which no one has been able to find.
The Free Colonists would pay well for anyone who can add one more death to his name.[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]小托尼经营着一个当地的强盗(Bandits)团伙，经常有人发现他藏身在废弃的空间站里。
他被认为比任何其他强盗(Bandits)被杀的次数都多，但由于他的克隆室，没有人能找到，他不断回来。
自由殖民者(Free Colonists)愿意为能给他的名字上再添一笔死亡的人支付丰厚的报酬。[-][/c]

Bring to a Bounty Hunter Office in trading station sectors in Pirates territory for a reward.

[c][D5D5D5]Savanth has been a thorn in the side of the Free Pirates for a number of years. Responsible for a number of bandit attacks on shipping lanes, he has now stepped up his attacks to include stations and civilian outposts.
The Free Pirates will pay for proof of his demise, although it is often not long until he returns in a freshly cloned body.[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF][b]通缉方:[/b][-][/c] [c][FFFF00]海盗(Pirates)[-][/c]

将其带到海盗领土内交易站区的赏金猎人办公室领取奖励。

[c][D5D5D5]萨万斯多年来一直是自由海盗的眼中钉。他负责多次针对航运路线的强盗(Bandits)袭击，现在他的袭击已经升级，包括对站点和平民前哨的攻击。
自由海盗将为他的死亡证据支付报酬，尽管他经常不久就会在一个新克隆的身体中回来。[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]Suspected of being a terrorist leader in the pirate gang known as the Bloodhunters, Marko made a name for himself for his extreme tactics.
He is wanted for his involvement in the asteroid bombardment of Intrazia Prime.[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]怀疑是被称为血猎者的海盗团伙中的恐怖主义领袖，马克以他的极端战术而声名狼藉。
他因参与对Intrazia Prime的小行星轰炸而遭到通缉。[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]Small Tony runs a local bandit gang and has frequently been spotted hiding out in derelict space stations.
Thought to have been killed more often than any other bandit, he keeps coming back for more thanks to his clone chamber which no one has been able to find.
The Free Pirates would pay well for anyone who can add one more death to his name.[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]小托尼经营着一个当地的强盗(Bandits)团伙，经常有人发现他藏身在废弃的空间站里。
他被认为比任何其他强盗(Bandits)被杀的次数都多，但由于他的克隆室，没有人能找到，他不断回来。
自由海盗愿意为能给他的名字上再添一笔死亡的人支付丰厚的报酬。[-][/c]

English:
A data pad containing the communication frequency of a specific trading station or factory. Can be used to help locate the factory.

[c][00FFFF]Requirements:[-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Must be friendly with Trade Federation.
-Must be in personal toolbar to initially activate the mission then can be stored in cargo.
-If you have changed playfields or restarted the game move any item into or out of your inventory to update the PDA.
-Activate the tracking mission under PDA > Trading.
-Place the required scanning probe in your personal toolbar.
-As long as the mission is currently active you will get a notification on your HUD if you enter a playfield that contains the factory you are tracking.
-Does not pinpoint the exact location, only whether or not it exists in your current planet, moon, or sector to save time having to fully explore the area.
-The trading frequency is reusable and can be activated again in the PDA.[/sup][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个数据板，包含特定交易站或工厂的通信频率。可以用来帮助定位工厂。

[c][00FFFF]要求:[-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-必须与贸易联盟保持友好关系。
-必须在个人工具栏中才能最初激活任务，之后可以存放在货物中。
-如果你更换了游戏场地或重新启动了游戏，将任何物品移入或移出你的库存以更新PDA。
-在PDA > 贸易下激活追踪任务。
-将所需的扫描探针放在你的个人工具栏中。
-只要任务当前处于激活状态，如果你进入包含你正在追踪的工厂的游戏场地，你将在你的HUD上收到通知。
-不会精确定位具体位置，只会告诉你它是否存在于你当前的行星、卫星或扇区，以节省完全探索该区域的时间。
-交易频率可重复使用，可以在PDA中再次激活。[-][/c][/sup]

English: See the Steam Workshop for more info on [c][00FFFF]Project Eden[-][/c] and [c][00FFFF]Reforged Eden[-][/c].
Chinese (simplified): 0. 查看创意工坊页面以获得 [c][00FFFF]伊甸园计划[-][/c] 和[c][00FFFF]重铸伊甸园[-][/c]的更多信息.

English: Check the [c][00FFFF]PDA[-][/c] (F1) for missions and the Empyriopedia.\nNew sections in the [c][00FFFF]Empyriopedia[-][/c] (F1) unlock as you explore and complete missions.
Chinese (simplified): 1. 查阅 [c][00FFFF]PDA[-][/c] (F1) 以访问任务和帝国霸业百科.\n [c][00FFFF]帝国霸业百科[-][/c] (F1) 会在你进行探索和完成任务时解锁新条目.

English: Strange alien drones have been spotted on the edge of the galaxy.
Chinese (simplified): 2. 有目击者声称星系边缘出现了奇怪的外星无人机

English: The [c][00FFFF]Project Eden: Getting Started[-][/c] section in the [c][00FFFF]Empyriopedia[-][/c] (F1) contains valuable survival tips.
Chinese (simplified): 3. [c][00FFFF]帝国霸业百科[-][/c] (F1)中的[c][00FFFF]伊甸园计划: 入门[-][/c] 章节写有宝贵的生存技巧提示

English: Project Eden is created by ravien_ff.\nReforged Galaxy is created by Vermillion.\nReforged Eden combines the two.
Chinese (simplified): 4. ravien_ff开发了了伊甸园计划.\nVermillion开发了重铸星系.\n重铸伊甸园将两者合二为一

English: [c][FFFF00]Need support on the scenario?[-][/c]\nYou can find assistance on the Steam Workshop page for the scenario.
Chinese (simplified): 5. [c][FFFF00]需要游玩本剧本的帮助?[-][/c]\n你可以在steam创意工坊中本mod的页面寻求帮助

English: [c][FFFF00]Want to report a game bug?[-][/c]\nPlease reproduce it in a unmodded, default game before reporting it to the Empyrion developers.
Chinese (simplified): 6. [c][FFFF00]想要向官方汇报Bug?[-][/c]\n请在无Mod的游戏本体内确保bug可以重复再进行上报.

English: Completing [c][00FFFF]Make Contact with Terran Forces[-][/c] under the Project Eden section of the PDA (F1) unlocks many more missions.
Chinese (simplified): 7. 完成 PDA中伊甸园计划部分的[c][00FFFF]与地球舰队会合[-][/c].后可以解锁更多任务

English: Neodymium is found on arid and desert planets. Titanium is found on snow and ice planets.
Chinese (simplified): 8. 钕可以在沙漠星球找到，钛可以在雪地和冰冻星球上找到

English: Sathium can often be found on barren planets.
Chinese (simplified): 9. 钑经常可以在荒芜星球上找到

English: A, F, and G class stars are usually easy difficulty habitable systems.\nD and M class stars are usually medium difficulty cold systems.\nO, B, and K class stars are usually hard difficulty hot systems.
Chinese (simplified): 10. A，F和G 型恒星往往代表着简单的宜居星球.\nD和M型恒星则是中等难度的寒冷星系.\nO，B，K型则往往是高难度的炎热星系.

English: You start the game with the Project Eden Guide which contains basic hints to get you started.
Chinese (simplified): 11. 伊甸园计划的开局提示能够让你快速入门

English: Cobalt can often be found in orbit or on the starting planet's moon.
Chinese (simplified): 12. 钴矿经常能在初始星球的轨道或是月球上找到

English: The star class listed in brackets on the galaxy map affects what you will find there.
Chinese (simplified): 13. 括号中的恒星种类决定了你可能遇见的星球种类

English: Erestrum is often found in cold star systems while zascosium is often found in hot star systems.
Chinese (simplified): 14. 锷经常出现在寒冷星系，而铡则出现在高温星系

English: You have the resources for a basic warp small vessel around your starting planet.\nYou have the resources for a basic warp capital vessel in your starting solar system.
Chinese (simplified): 15. 你可以在初始星球附近找到足够的材料来帮助你进行星系内翘曲跳跃\n初始星系内有足够的材料可以可以让你造出可以进行基础星系间跳跃的主力舰

English: In Eden you can find many missions off the beaten path.\nDon't be afraid to explore, you never know what you might find.
Chinese (simplified): 16. 在伊甸园计划中你会在你走过的路上发现各种各样的任务\n不要畏惧探索，你永远也不知道会有什么惊喜

English: You can use a warp capable small vessel to explore your starting solar system.\nYou can use a warp capable capital vessel to explore the galaxy.
Chinese (simplified): 17. 装有翘曲驱动器的小型飞船可以用来探索本太阳系\n装有翘曲驱动器的主力舰则可以探索整个星系

English: The solar system map contains information about resource asteroids in space and ore deposits on planets as well as additional information on each sector, planet, or moon.
Chinese (simplified): 18. 太阳系星图包含了太空中小行星和地表的矿床的信息，同时也有关于星区/行星和卫星的总览

English: Project Eden Research Vessels are important to the Project Eden missions.\nThey can be found as a blue triangle on the solar system map in the starting systems or in some habitable systems in neutral territory.
Chinese (simplified): 19. 研究船对伊甸园计划的任务十分重要，他们往往出现在初始星系和中立区域的宜居星系内，在太阳系星图内以蓝色三角形标注

English: There are 15 starting planets in Project Eden ranging in difficulty from beginner to ultra hard.\nThere are 5 starting solar systems.
Chinese (simplified): 20. 伊甸园计划有15个由易到难的初始星球，初始星系则有5个

English: Your difficulty settings and starting planet will have a large effect on how hard it will be. Take your time when setting up settings for a new game.
Chinese (simplified): 21. 初始星球的难度设置会很大程度上影响开局的玩法，在设置时一定要三思

English: Space is dangerous. Keep pinging your detector and watching for enemy patrol vessels or drones.\nSpace stations can call for reinforcements when attacked.
Chinese (simplified): 22. 太空充满了危险，善用扫描仪来时刻关注敌对巡逻飞船和无人机的动向\n空间站可能会在受到攻击时呼叫增援

English: The starting solar systems are Alpha, Beta, Delta, Epsilon, and Rogue.
Chinese (simplified): 23. 五个初始星系分别是Alpha，Beta，Delta，Epsilon和 Rogue.

English: You can change your difficulty settings at any time from the resume game menu.
Chinese (simplified): 24. 你可以随时在主菜单的回到游戏页面修改单机难度设置

English: You can change various scenario settings in the briefing rooms at UCH Research Vessels.
Chinese (simplified): 25. 在创意工坊订阅Project Eden Admin Control可以让你更容易地修改服务器设置

English: The Project Eden galaxy contains over 20,000 star systems with dozens of new planets, moons, and sectors.
Chinese (simplified): 26. 伊甸园计划的星系拥有超过20000个恒星系，以及大量的新星球，卫星和星区

English: Use the in-game backup feature to quickly create a copy of your save game.\nResuming a backup save makes that backup save your current one. Save an extra backup right away if you want to still maintain a backup save.
Chinese (simplified): 27. 利用游戏内备份机制来生成当前存档的额外备份

English: Mining the asteroid a space station is anchored to is considered an act of war regardless of reputation level.
Chinese (simplified): 28. 无论声望如何，挖掘空间站锚定的小行星都将被认为是宣战行为

English: Always save your blueprints as save games can become corrupt.
Chinese (simplified): 29. 永远记得保存飞船蓝图，游戏存档随时都有可能损坏\n周期性备份存档是个好习惯

English: A rare ore has been discovered floating above lava lakes on some lava planets.
Chinese (simplified): 30. 有些岩浆星球的岩浆湖上会有悬浮的稀有矿物

English: The Decay star cluster is where the Ancient Progenitors are from.
Chinese (simplified): 31. 腐化星团是先祖的发源地

English: Check the Faction checkbox in the galaxy map to see faction territories.\nYou can find different things in different territories. Some factions fiercly guard their territory.
Chinese (simplified): 32. 在星系图中勾选领地选框来查看所属派系\n你会在不同派系领地中发现不同的东西. 有些派系会严密防守他们的星区

English: Many missions do not show up in the PDA at all. You will have to explore to find them.
Chinese (simplified): 33.很多任务都不会直接显示在PDA中，你需要自己在探索中发现

English: By holding down a combination of CTRL SHIFT and or ALT (depends on keybindings) and using the WASD C and Space keys while holding left click you can quickly move or pan the camera in the galaxy map.
Chinese (simplified): 34.同时按住Ctrl+Shift可以更快的移动星图镜头

English: Some rare devices cannot be repaired by a repair bay or station services and must be manually replaced.
Chinese (simplified): 35.某些稀有设备不能被空间站服务或是维修平台修复，必须要手动重新安装

English: Many NPC factions are player created such as the Brotherhood of Farr, the Skaar, or the Kriel.
Chinese (simplified): 36.许多NPC派系都是玩家创建的，例如Farr，Skarr以及克里尔帝国

English: Bounty Hunter Offices will buy insignias you find on Bandit and Raider patrol vessels or by killing bounties.
Chinese (simplified): 37.赏金官员会购买你从土匪，劫掠者飞船上找到或是击杀任务得来的徽章

English: Distribution Centers are found in the Trade Station sectors of some of the major factions.\nVisit a Distribution Headquarters in Trade Federation territory to accept cargo delivery contracts.
Chinese (simplified): 38.配送中心可以在主要派系的某些交易站点附近找到，在贸易联邦的领地找到配送中心来接受货运任务

English: Single player games will automatically get updates for the scenario.\nDedicated servers must update the scenario manually.
Chinese (simplified): 39.单人游戏的场景会由steam自动更新，服务器就得手动上传了

English: The Lead Researchers and Research Computers on UCH Research Vessels offer important services and missions.
Chinese (simplified): 40.UCH研究船上的首席研究员和研究计算机可能会提供非常重要的任务信息

English: You can continue to earn unlock points after level 25 through missions or loot.
Chinese (simplified): 41.你可以通过任务或是战利品在25级之后继续获得额外的解锁点数

English: Hydroponics Bays allow for much easier farming by harvesting 9 crops at once.
Chinese (simplified): 42.水培箱可以让你一次收获9株作物，大大简化了种植的流程

English: Missing a mission item? Check your connected inventory or look for a dropbox next to your character.\nMany mission items are flagged to not drop on death.
Chinese (simplified): 43.找不到任务物品？看看你连接到的容器吧

English: Some individuals may have rumors or missions for you. It can pay to take a look around.
Chinese (simplified): 44.有些NPC可能会提供传言或是支线任务，可以花点时间去进行对话

English: Your armor becomes less effective at mitigating incoming damage the more damaged it is.\nArmor at half durability will give half the protection.
Chinese (simplified): 46.护甲的减伤能力随着受到损害的增加而降低.\n简而言之一半耐久的护甲也只能提供一半的保护.

English: Read. Read tooltips. Read playfield descriptions. Read dialog. And read the PDA.\nMany questions can be answered by simply reading.
Chinese (simplified): 47. 阅读！多多留意工具的提示，地图上的描述，对话文本，以及最最重要的PDA.\n很多问题只要一点小小的阅读能力就能解决.

English: While in creative mode no POIs, patrol vessels, ore deposits, or NPCs will spawn.
Chinese (simplified): 48. 创造模式中并不会生成POI，巡逻船，矿床以及NPC

English: Make sure you keep the scenario up to date on your server.\nSee the Workshop for update instructions and troubleshooting.
Chinese (simplified): 记得将你服务器上的场景更新为最新版\n在工坊页面查看更新日志和故障排除指南

English: Alerts: <#ff0000>Low fuel. Requires at least 300 fuel per extractor.</color>
Chinese (simplified): 警报:<color=#ff0000>燃料不足。每个提取器至少需要300单位燃料。</color>

English: Alerts: <#ff0000>Low fuel. Requires at least fuel per extractor.</color> <#ffff00>Storage full.</color>
Chinese (simplified): 警报:<color=#ff0000>燃料不足。每个提取器至少需要一定量的燃料。</color><color=#ffff00>存储已满。</color>

English: Welcome to our research vessel. What brings you all the way out here to {0}? As for us we are currently studying a nearby star cluster.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我们的研究船。是什么风把你吹到{0}这里来的？至于我们，目前我们正在研究附近的一个恒星团。

English: Welcome to my research vessel. We are currently performing research on the star in this system. If you have any questions I'd be happy to answer them, but please don't take up too much of my crew's time as they are behind schedule.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我的研究船。我们目前正在对这个星系中的恒星进行研究。如果你有任何问题，我很乐意回答，但请不要占用我船员太多时间，因为他们已经落后于计划了。

English: Hello. We are here in {0} performing scans of nearby planets in hopes of setting up a mining outpost.
Chinese (simplified): 你好。我们在{0}这里对附近行星进行扫描，希望建立一个采矿前哨站。

English: Welcome aboard. I am the captain of this research vessel. You will have to excuse us as we are quite busy running scans on interstellar gases and anomalies.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎上船。我是这艘研究船的船长。我们目前正在忙于对星际气体和异常现象进行扫描，所以请见谅。

English: -Then run it again! The diagnostic must have missed something!\nOh, hi, I didn't see you there. We were recently attacked by a Zirax Battlecarrier so we have a lot of repairs left to do.
Chinese (simplified): 那就再运行一次！诊断肯定漏掉了一些东西！\n哦，你好，我没看到你在那里。我们最近被兹瑞克斯战斗航母攻击了，所以我们还有很多修理工作要做。

English: We're currently scanning for resources in {0}. Is there something I can help you with?
Chinese (simplified): 我们目前正在{0}扫描资源。有什么我可以帮忙的吗？

English: Welcome to our research vessel. What brings you all the way out here to {0}? As for us we are currently studying a nearby star cluster.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我们的研究船。是什么风把你吹到{0}这里来的？至于我们，目前我们正在研究附近的一个恒星团。

English: I came to {0} looking for work. What about you?
I miss the forests of my homeworld. I'm trying to save up enough money to visit.
Chinese (simplified): 我想念我的母星上的森林。我正试图攒够钱去拜访。

English: My access card is broken again.
I'd watch out for pickpockets if I were you.
Chinese (simplified): 如果我是你，我会小心扒手。

English: Don't see many of your kind around here.
Chinese (simplified): 这里不常看到你这样的人。

English: What brings you to the Badlands? Nevermind, I don't want to know. Nobody ever has a good reason to come out here.
Chinese (simplified): 你来荒地有什么事？算了，我不想知道。来这里的人从来没有什么好理由。

English: I ran out of job prospects in Prosperity so I came here looking for work. Found only trouble.
Chinese (simplified): 我在繁荣之地用尽了工作机会，所以我来到这里寻找工作。找到的只有麻烦。

English: Heed my advice and stay away from upstairs.
Chinese (simplified): 听从我的建议，远离楼上。

English: These games are rigged. I know because I'm the one who rigged them.
Chinese (simplified): 这些游戏是被操纵的。我知道，因为我就是操纵它们的人。

English: Bring out yer dead! Bring out yer dead!
Chinese (simplified): 把你的死者抬出来！把你的死者抬出来！

English: I'm concerned with how fast the Syndicate has been expanding. Pretty soon there will be no more room for small time smugglers like myself. I mean, my totally legit cargo hauling business.
Chinese (simplified): 我对联合会扩张的速度感到担忧。很快，像我这样的小规模走私者就没有空间了。我的意思是，我完全合法的货物运输业务。

English: Keep to yourself and nobody will bother you.
Chinese (simplified): 管好你自己，就不会有人来烦你。

English: You best keep walking, tough guy.
You want to buy some death sticks?
If you're looking for work I hear Underground Music is looking for a courier.
Chinese (simplified): 如果你在找工作，我听说地下音乐正在寻找一名信使。
...塞特什守卫的鼻子在滴水。哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈！

English: I don't know you and I don't want to know you.
Chinese (simplified): 我不认识你，也不想认识你。

English: I used to be an  adventurer like you then I took a look at my life and turned it around.
Chinese (simplified): 我曾经像你一样是个冒险家，然后我审视了自己的生活并改变了它。

English: No one here is exactly what they appear.
Chinese (simplified): 这里没有人是他们表面上看起来的那样。

English: Smuggler? Pirate? Slaver? Drug dealer? Which are you?
Chinese (simplified): 走私者？海盗？奴隶贩子？毒品贩子？你是哪一种？

English: I heard the Syndicate is ran by someone they call The Raven.
Chinese (simplified): 我听说联合会是由一个他们称作“乌鸦”的人掌控的。

English: I-I don't w-w-want any trouble pl-please!
Chinese (simplified): 我...我不...不想惹麻烦，拜...拜托了！

English: Have you heard the good word of Farr?
Enjoying your visit to this freeport?
Chinese (simplified): 你喜欢这次自由港的旅程吗？

English: Stay away from gas clouds in space.
There's been a lot more smugglers coming through here lately. Something is going on.
Chinese (simplified): 最近这里来了很多走私者。一定有什么事在发生。

English: Music? Entertainment? Food and drink? The Freeport here in {0} has it all!
Chinese (simplified): 音乐？娱乐？食物和饮料？这个在 {0} 的自由港应有尽有！

English: I really, really hate it here in {0}.
Chinese (simplified): 狗屎，{0} 这里真的很讨厌！

English: If you're not paying me stay away from me.
Chinese (simplified): 如果你不打算付钱，那就离我远点。

English: No one comes here by accident. Why are you here, friend?
Chinese (simplified): 没有人偶然来到这里。你来这儿，朋友，有什么事吗？

English: Take my advice and don't make the guards angry.
Chinese (simplified): 听我一句劝，别惹守卫生气。

English: Colonist stations are popping up all over. Ripe for the raiding!
Chinese (simplified): 殖民者站正在各地涌现。正是掠夺的好时机！

English: You want to have a go at me?
Did you hear what happened in the Sea of Silence?
Chinese (simplified): 你听说沉默之海发生了什么吗？

English: A group from the Omicron Raiders came through here last week. Roudy bunch but tipped good. Guess they got a good haul.
Chinese (simplified): 上周一群Omicron掠夺者从这里经过。粗鲁的一群人，但给了不错的小费。

English: You look like you could use a drink. Head on over to PAX Purgatory.
Chinese (simplified): 你看起来可能需要喝一杯。去PAX炼狱吧。

English: Keep a tight grip on your coin purse.
There's a secret way into the VIP lounge. No, I won't tell you where it is.
Chinese (simplified): 有一个秘密通道可以进入VIP休息室。不，我不会告诉你它在哪里。

Japanese: ベースアタックドローン(小)
デザートワームリーダー

Vietnamese: Cửa bọc thép tự động 2 (chiều dọc)

English: You have a Closed Fracture.\nApply a Bandage, Health Pack to treat, or a Regeneration Kit, Trauma Kit or use a Medical Trauma Table to heal!
Deutsch: Geschlossener Bruch! Nutze Bandagen, ein Trauma Kit oder eine Medizinstation Typ 2!
Français:
Fracture 
- Bandages 
- Kit trauma 
- Poste médical T3
Italiano: Hai un Frattura. Utilizza una Fasciatura, un Kit per Traumi o un Stazione Medica Classe 2!
Spanish: Tienes una fractura. ¡Usa vendajes, un kit para traumatismos o una estación médica tipo 2!
Portuguese (Brazil): Você esta com uma Fratura Interna! Use as Ataduras, um Kit Trauma ou vá ate uma Estação Médica Tipo 2!
Polish: Złamałeś kończynę. Użyj bandażu, zestawu pourazowego albo stacji medycznej typu 2!
